%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Frontotemporal%20dementia%20symptoms%20include%20aphasia%20and%20mood%20changes.%20Learn%20more%20about%20the%20disease's%20causes%20and%20treatment.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221416%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wendy%20Williams%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d7c0b790413ab8e1d639d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221903%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECalvin%20Gayle%20via%20Lifetime%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFrontotemporal%20dementia%20is%20a%20form%20of%20cognitive%20decline%20that%20can%20cause%20memory%20loss%20and%20personality%20changes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETalk%20show%20host%20Wendy%20Williams%20and%20actor%20Bruce%20Willis%20have%20both%20been%20diagnosed%20with%20the%20condition.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20can%20occur%20at%20a%20younger%20age%20than%20Alzheimer's%2C%20typically%20in%20people%20aged%2040%20to%2060%20years%20old.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBroadcast%20media%20star%20Wendy%20Williams%20has%20been%20diagnosed%20with%20frontotemporal%20dementia%20and%20primary%20progressive%20aphasia%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prnewswire.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fwendy-williams-diagnosed-with-primary-progressive-aphasia-and-dementia-302068851.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20her%20care%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20related%20neurodegenerative%20conditions%20can%20both%20cause%20issues%20with%20memory%20and%20behavior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams'%20diagnosis%20was%20announced%20February%2022.%20The%20former%20talk%20show%20host%20had%20previously%20stepped%20down%20from%20her%20namesake%20show%20after%20reported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwendy-williams-has-serious-health-complications-wont-return-to-show-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bserious%20complications%26quot%3B%20of%20other%20health%20conditions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-symptoms%2Foveractive-thyroid%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGraves'%20Disease%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20Williams%20had%20begun%20to%20show%20signs%20of%20erratic%20behavior%2C%20confusion%2C%20and%20loss%20of%20words%2C%20according%20to%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20many%20individuals%20diagnosed%20with%20aphasia%20and%20frontotemporal%20dementia%20face%20stigma%20and%20misunderstanding%2C%20particularly%20when%20they%20begin%20to%20exhibit%20behavioral%20changes%20but%20have%20not%20yet%20received%20a%20diagnosis%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20condition%20has%20received%20more%20public%20awareness%20due%20to%20other%20high-profile%20cases%20in%20celebrities%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbruce-willis-diagnosis-frontotemporal-dementia-symptoms-treatment-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBruce%20Willis%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whose%20family%20announced%20his%20diagnosis%20in%20February%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20currently%20no%20cure%20or%20treatment%20for%20the%20condition%2C%20and%20it%20is%20known%20to%20progress%20over%20time%2C%20causing%20further%20decline%20in%20patients'%20ability%20to%20make%20decisions%20and%20communicate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESymptoms%20of%20frontotemporal%20dementia%3A%20difficulty%20communicating%2C%20changes%20to%20mood%20and%20behavior%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFrontotemporal%20dementia%20refers%20to%20a%20group%20of%20disorders%20caused%20by%20nerve%20cell%20damage%20to%20areas%20of%20the%20brain%20behind%20the%20forehead%20(in%20the%20frontal%20lobe)%20and%20behind%20the%20ears%20(in%20the%20temporal%20lobes).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20parts%20of%20the%20brain%20help%20control%20language%20and%20behavior%2C%20so%20people%20with%20the%20condition%20can%20experience%20symptoms%20such%20as%20difficulty%20communicating%2C%20impulsive%20actions%2C%20or%20major%20personality%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mayoclinic.org%2Fdiseases-conditions%2Fprimary-progressive-aphasia%2Fsymptoms-causes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrimary%20progressive%20aphasia%20falls%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20FTD.%3C%2Fa%3E%20It%20is%20a%20condition%20that%20affects%20a%20person's%20ability%20to%20communicate.%20Symptoms%20begin%20slowly%20and%20gradually%2C%20but%20over%20time%20can%20cause%20people%20to%20lose%20the%20ability%20to%20speak%2C%20write%2C%20or%20understand%20language%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Mayo%20Clinic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrontotemporal%20dementia%20can%20also%20have%20symptoms%20such%20as%20memory%20loss%2C%20but%20unlike%20other%20forms%20of%20dementia%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falzheimers-and-dementia-misconceptions-and-surprising-facts-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlzheimer's%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20typically%20occurs%20in%20younger%20people.%20Most%20cases%20of%20frontotemporal%20dementia%20are%20in%20people%20aged%2045%20to%2064%2C%20and%20it%20is%20the%20most%20common%20form%20of%20cognitive%20decline%20in%20people%20under%2060%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theaftd.org%2Fwhat-is-ftd%2Fdisease-overview%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAssociation%20for%20Frontotemporal%20Degeneration%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-frontotemporal-dementia-ftd-symptoms-causes-treatment%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708651171000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d7bb8d90413ab8e1d636f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-frontotemporal-dementia-ftd-symptoms-causes-treatment%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Frontotemporal%20dementia%20and%20a%20related%20condition%20called%20aphasia%20have%20symptoms%20such%20as%20difficulty%20communicating%2C%20loss%20of%20words%2C%20and%20erratic%20behavior.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22glandsverk%40insider.com%20(Gabby%20Landsverk)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-frontotemporal-dementia-ftd-symptoms-causes-treatment%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22American%20company%20makes%20historic%20Moon%20landing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708650802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FE159%2Fproduction%2F_132698675_52342438613_5ee4f33cf1_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-68377730%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Intuitive%20Machines%20completes%20the%20first%20ever%20lunar%20touchdown%20by%20a%20privately%20built%20spacecraft.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-68377730%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-68377730.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-68377730.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biden%20Meets%20Putin%20Critic%20Navalny's%20Family%20In%20California%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20had%20a%20private%2C%20emotional%20meeting%20with%20the%20widow%20and%20daughter%20of%20Alexei%20Navalny%20in%20California%20on%20Thursday%2C%20as%20his%20administration%20announced%20fresh%20sanctions%20against%20Russia%20over%20the%20death%20of%20the%20Kremlin%20opposition%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20visit%20at%20a%20hotel%20in%20San%20Francisco%20came%20as%20the%20White%20House%20backed%20Navalny's%20mother%20in%20her%20fight%20to%20retrieve%20her%20son's%20body%2C%20which%20Russian%20authorities%20have%20refused%20to%20release%20days%20after%20he%20died%20in%20an%20Arctic%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavalny's%20team%20says%20the%2047-year-old%2C%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin's%20most%20outspoken%20critic%2C%20was%20murdered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20could%20be%20seen%20hugging%20Yulia%20Navalnaya%2C%20Navalny's%20widow%2C%20and%20leaning%20forward%20as%20he%20spoke%20with%20her%20and%20daughter%20Dasha%2C%20a%20student%20at%20Stanford%20University%2C%20in%20images%20released%20by%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EToday%2C%20I%20met%20with%20Yulia%20and%20Dasha%20Navalnaya%20%E2%80%93%20Aleksey%20Navalny's%20loved%20ones%20%E2%80%93%20to%20express%20my%20condolences%20for%20their%20devastating%20loss.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAleksey's%20legacy%20of%20courage%20will%20live%20on%20in%20Yulia%20and%20Dasha%2C%20and%20the%20countless%20people%20across%20Russia%20fighting%20for%20democracy%20and%20human%20rights.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FaiCcgTrws3%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FaiCcgTrws3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20President%20Biden%20(%40POTUS)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPOTUS%2Fstatus%2F1760752933866512580%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president's%20own%20history%20of%20loss%20--%20his%20first%20wife%20and%20his%20infant%20daughter%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20car%20crash%20in%201972%2C%20while%20his%20son%20Beau%20died%20of%20cancer%20in%202015%20--%20has%20seen%20him%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20America's%20Consoler-in-Chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%2C%20he%20said%20the%20two%20women%20were%20emulating%20Navalny's%20%26quot%3Bincredible%20courage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYulia%20Navalnaya%2C%20who%20has%20vowed%20to%20continue%20her%20late%20husband's%20opposition%20to%20Putin%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20giving%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Polar%20Wolf'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20administration%20announced%20Thursday%20that%20it%20would%20sanction%20more%20than%20500%20targets%20in%20Russia's%20%26quot%3Bwar%20machine%26quot%3B%20to%20mark%20the%20second%20anniversary%20of%20the%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20and%20in%20response%20to%20Navalny's%20death%2C%20for%20which%20the%20president%20stressed%20Putin%20was%20%26quot%3Bresponsible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20have%20imposed%20a%20slew%20of%20sanctions%20on%20Russia%20since%20it%20invaded%20Ukraine%20in%20February%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavalny%2C%20who%20died%20on%20February%2016%2C%20galvanized%20mass%20protests%20against%20Putin%2C%20winning%20popularity%20with%20a%20series%20of%20investigations%20into%20state%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20poisoned%20with%20a%20Soviet-era%20nerve%20agent%20in%202020%2C%20then%20jailed%20in%202021%20after%20returning%20to%20Russia%20following%20a%20period%20of%20treatment%20in%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20sentenced%20to%2019%20years%20in%20prison%20on%20extremism%20charges%20and%20sent%20to%20IK-3%2C%20a%20harsh%20penal%20colony%20beyond%20the%20Arctic%20Circle%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BPolar%20Wolf.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWestern%20governments%20and%20Russian%20opposition%20figures%20have%20accused%20the%20Kremlin%20of%20being%20responsible%20for%20his%20death%2C%20with%20an%20outraged%20Biden%20previously%20blaming%20Putin%20and%20his%20%26quot%3Bthugs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMother's%20plea%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20people%20have%20been%20detained%20in%20Russia%20in%20recent%20days%20at%20events%20to%20pay%20tribute%20to%20Navalny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20mother%2C%20Lyudmila%20Navalnaya%2C%20travelled%20to%20Russia's%20Far%20North%20the%20morning%20after%20her%20son's%20death%20was%20announced%2C%20hoping%20to%20retrieve%20his%20body.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20days%20officials%20refused%20her%20access%2C%20prompting%20her%20to%20make%20a%20video%20appeal%20directly%20to%20Putin%20himself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%20she%20said%20she%20had%20been%20shown%20Navalny's%20body%20in%20a%20morgue%20in%20Salekhard%2C%20the%20nearest%20town%20to%20the%20remote%20prison.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20in%20a%20video%20released%20on%20social%20media%20by%20Navalny's%20team%2C%20she%20said%20investigators%20wanted%20her%20son%20to%20be%20buried%20%26quot%3Bsecretly%2C%20without%20a%20chance%20to%20say%20goodbye.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20blackmailing%20me%2C%20they%20put%20conditions%20for%20where%2C%20when%20and%20how%20Alexei%20should%20be%20buried.%20This%20is%20illegal%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20want%20to%20take%20me%20to%20the%20edge%20of%20a%20cemetery%20to%20a%20fresh%20grave%20and%20say%3A%20Here%20is%20where%20your%20son%20lies.%20I%20am%20against%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20that%20for%20those%20of%20you%20for%20whom%20Alexei%20is%20dear%2C%20for%20everyone%20for%20whom%20his%20death%20became%20a%20personal%20tragedy%2C%20to%20have%20the%20possibility%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20recorded%20the%20video%20because%20investigators%20were%20%26quot%3Bthreatening%26quot%3B%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLooking%20me%20in%20the%20eye%2C%20they%20said%20that%20if%20I%20do%20not%20agree%20to%20a%20secret%20funeral%20they'll%20do%20something%20with%20my%20son's%20body...%20I%20ask%20for%20my%20son's%20body%20to%20be%20given%20to%20me%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavalny's%20mother%20also%20said%20that%20investigators%20told%20her%20they%20knew%20the%20cause%20of%20death%20but%20did%20not%20say%20what%20it%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kremlin%20has%20refused%20to%20say%20when%20the%20body%20will%20be%20handed%20over%20and%20has%20branded%20Western%20accusations%20as%20%26quot%3Bhysterical.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Russians%20need%20to%20give%20her%20back%20her%20son%2C%26quot%3B%20US%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesman%20John%20Kirby%20told%20reporters%20Thursday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%20has%20remained%20silent%20on%20the%20death%20of%20his%20main%20political%20opponent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavalny's%20spokesman%20Kira%20Yarmysh%20said%20a%20medical%20report%20on%20the%20death%20shown%20to%20Lyudmila%20Navalnaya%20%26quot%3Bstated%20that%20the%20cause%20of%20death%20was%20natural.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708650720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Faekrouuo_biden-met-navalny-widow-wife_625x300_23_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Falexei-navalny-death-joe-biden-met-with-putin-critic-alexei-navalny-wife-daughter-to-express-heartfelt-condolences-5109412%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Joe%20Biden%20met%20privately%20in%20California%20on%20Thursday%20with%20the%20widow%20and%20daughter%20of%20Kremlin%20opposition%20leader%20Alexei%20Navalny%2C%20who%20died%20in%20a%20Russian%20prison%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Falexei-navalny-death-joe-biden-met-with-putin-critic-alexei-navalny-wife-daughter-to-express-heartfelt-condolences-5109412%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Falexei-navalny-death-joe-biden-met-with-putin-critic-alexei-navalny-wife-daughter-to-express-heartfelt-condolences-5109412%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Falexei-navalny-death-joe-biden-met-with-putin-critic-alexei-navalny-wife-daughter-to-express-heartfelt-condolences-5109412%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Exclusive%3A%20Russia-linked%20smear%20campaign%20against%20Hunter%20Biden%20began%20earlier%20than%20previously%20thought%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hunter%20Biden%20in%202022.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F649322241465b60019987d4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWASHINGTON%2C%20DC%20April%2018%2C%202022%3A%20Hunter%20Biden%20during%20the%20White%20House%20Easter%20Egg%20Roll%20on%20the%20South%20Lawn%20on%20April%2018%2C%202022..%3Cp%3EDemetrius%20Freeman%2FThe%20Washington%20Post%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20former%20KGB%20agent%20handed%20a%20thumb%20drive%20with%20Hunter%20Biden%20disinformation%20to%20an%20aide%20for%20former%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Mike%20Pompeo%20at%20a%20gala%20event%20in%20May%202019.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20former%20KGB%20agent%20also%20presented%20the%20same%20disinformation%20to%20Justice%20Department%20officials%20in%20January%202019.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20presentation%20marks%20the%20earliest%20known%20instance%20of%20a%20Russia-linked%20source%20pushing%20allegations%20about%20Hunter%20Biden%20and%20Burisma.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20thumb%20drive%20handed%20by%20a%20foreign%20national%20to%20an%20aide%20traveling%20with%20then-Secretary%20of%20State%20Mike%20Pompeo%20in%202019%20suggests%20that%20efforts%20by%20Russia-linked%20actors%20to%20influence%20the%202020%20US%20presidential%20election%20with%20Hunter%20Biden%20disinformation%20began%20earlier%20and%20were%20broader%20in%20scope%20than%20has%20previously%20been%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20two%20sources%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20a%20thumb%20drive%20containing%20poorly%20sourced%20allegations%20about%20Hunter%20Biden%20and%20his%20work%20for%20Burisma%2C%20a%20Ukrainian%20energy%20company%2C%20was%20thrust%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20one%20of%20Pompeo's%20aides%20at%20the%20conservative%20Claremont%20Institute's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.claremont.org%2Fevents%2F40-annual-gala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E40th%20anniversary%20gala%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20Beverly%20Hills%20on%20May%2011%2C%202019.%20The%20man%20pushing%20the%20thumb%20drive%20was%20a%20citizen%20of%20an%20Eastern%20European%20country%20and%20a%20guest%20of%20Claremont.%20He%20was%20also%2C%20for%20a%20time%2C%20an%20FBI%20confidential%20informant%2C%20with%20the%20code%20name%20%26quot%3BRollie.%26quot%3B%20His%20true%20name%20is%20known%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20which%20is%20only%20identifying%20him%20as%20Rollie%20in%20order%20to%20protect%20sources%20who%20provided%20information%20for%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERollie%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20seemed%20unconcerned%20about%20potential%20exposure.%20At%20first%2C%20he%20denied%20knowing%20anything%20about%20Pompeo%20when%20contacted%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20But%20when%20BI%20sent%20him%20a%20photo%20of%20him%20at%20the%20gala%20with%20Pompeo%2C%20he%20admitted%20that%20he%20had%20been%20there.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20publish%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20advertising%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22759%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Former%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Mike%20Pompeo%20with%20%26quot%3BRollie%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d7e32f6080194819f998af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221176%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Mike%20Pompeo%20with%20%26quot%3BRollie%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20former%20KGB%20agent%2C%20at%20a%20Claremont%20Institute%20gala%20on%20May%2011%2C%202019.%20That%20evening%2C%20Rollie%20passed%20a%20thumb%20drive%20containing%20disinformation%20about%20Hunter%20Biden%20and%20Burisma%20to%20a%20Pompeo%20aide.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20obtained%20by%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERollie%20told%20associates%20and%20confirmed%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he%20had%20once%20served%20in%20the%20KGB%2C%20the%20Soviet%20intelligence%20agency%2C%20before%20swearing%20loyalty%20to%20the%20country%20where%20he%20now%20resides.%20The%20thumb%20drive%20that%20Rollie%20gave%20Pompeo's%20aide%20contained%20some%20of%20the%20same%20material%20that%20Rollie%20had%20presented%20weeks%20earlier%2C%20in%20January%202019%2C%20in%20a%20briefing%20to%20Justice%20Department%20officials%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20interested%20in%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20Rollie%20said%20when%20asked%20over%20WhatsApp%20about%20the%20briefing.%20He%20denied%20that%20he%20gave%20anyone%20a%20thumb%20drive%20at%20the%20Claremont%20Institute%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20obtained%20a%20copy%20of%20slides%20that%20accompanied%20Rollie's%20January%202019%20presentation.%20They%20accuse%20Hunter%20Biden%20and%20his%20business%20associates%20of%20engaging%20in%20money%20laundering%2C%20tax%20evasion%2C%20and%20fraud.%20Rollie's%20slides%20offer%20a%20labyrinthine%20wire%20chart%2C%20clippings%20from%20old%20news%20articles%2C%20and%20a%20potpourri%20of%20links%20including%20various%20Ukrainian%20and%20Russian%20websites.%20President%20Biden's%20first%20name%20is%20repeatedly%20misspelled%20as%20%26quot%3BJosef.%26quot%3B%20They%20contain%20no%20evidence%20of%20criminal%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20according%20to%20a%20disclosure%20prepared%20by%20FBI%20whistleblower%20Johnathan%20Buma%2C%20Rollie's%20handler%2C%20the%20material%20was%20taken%20seriously%20enough%20to%20be%20passed%20on%20to%20FBI%20agents%20in%20Delaware%20who%20were%20investigating%20Hunter%20Biden.%20Also%20included%20were%20some%20Ukrainian-language%20backup%20materials%20which%20Business%20Insider%20has%20not%20reviewed.%20Rollie%20confirmed%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he%20had%20prior%20contact%20with%20the%20FBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Rollie%20presentation%20sheds%20new%20light%20on%20the%20timeline%20of%20efforts%20by%20Russia%20and%20by%20operatives%20for%20Donald%20Trump%20to%20seed%20allegations%20about%20Joe%20Biden's%20relationship%20to%20Burisma%20with%20the%20media%20and%20government%20authorities.%20While%20questions%20about%20the%20propriety%20of%20Hunter's%20lucrative%20Burisma%20work%20in%20Ukraine%20were%20raised%20by%20the%20New%20York%20Times%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2015%2F12%2F09%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fcorruption-ukraine-joe-biden-son-hunter-biden-ties.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20early%20as%202015%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20explored%20in%20a%202018%20book%20by%20conservative%20author%20Peter%20Schweizer%2C%20they%20didn't%20explode%20into%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20political%20conversation%20until%20March%202019.%20It%20was%20during%20that%20month%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-impeachment-inquiry%2Fgiuliani-says-state-dept-vowed-investigate-after-he-gave-ukraine-n1061931%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERudy%20Giuliani%20gave%20Pompeo%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20folder%20of%20Hunter%20Biden%20material%20that%20he%20obtained%20from%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20right-wing%20investigative%20reporter%20John%20Solomon%20began%20publishing%20a%20series%20of%20columns%20about%20Hunter%20Biden%20and%20Burisma%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fhomenews%2Fnews%2F483600-the-hills-review-of-john-solomons-columns-on-ukraine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Hill%3C%2Fa%3E.%20One%20month%20later%2C%20in%20April%202019%2C%20Hunter%20abandoned%20his%20laptop%20at%20a%20Delaware%20repair%20shop%2C%20eventually%20leading%20to%20a%20wave%20of%20revelations%20in%20October%202020%20that%20included%20information%20about%20his%20business%20dealings%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Hunter-Burisma%20material%20that%20was%20presented%20in%20January%202019%2C%20and%20again%20on%20the%20thumb%20drive%20given%20to%20Pompeo's%20aide%20in%20May%202019%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20earliest%20known%20case%20of%20Burisma-related%20disinformation%20of%20foreign%20origin%20being%20ingested%20and%20apparently%20taken%20seriously%20by%20members%20of%20the%20US%20intelligence%20community.%20It%20also%20suggests%20a%20third%20channel%20of%202020%20disinformation%20moving%20from%20East%20to%20West%2C%20one%20that%20is%20separate%20from%20the%20previously%20known%20efforts%20that%20went%20through%20Giuliani%20and%20Alexander%20Smirnov%2C%20another%20FBI%20informant%20with%20ties%20to%20Russia%20and%20Eastern%20Europe.%20Smirnov%20was%20indicted%20last%20week%20for%20lying%20to%20the%20FBI%20about%20Hunter%20Biden.%20Prosecutors%20have%20claimed%20in%20court%20filings%20that%20Smirnov%20has%20extensive%20ties%20to%20Russian%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20easy%20to%20see%20why%20Hunter%20Biden's%20critics%20have%20focused%20on%20Burisma.%20The%20energy%20company%20paid%20Biden%20around%20%24600%2C000%20a%20year%20during%20a%20period%20that%20overlapped%20with%20his%20father's%20vice%20presidency.%20It's%20unclear%20what%20the%20company%20got%20for%20their%20money%20beyond%20the%20ability%20to%20brag%20about%20an%20indirect%20line%20into%20the%20White%20House.%20But%20almost%20five%20years%20after%20his%20departure%20from%20the%20board%2C%20Hunter%20Biden%20was%20never%20charged%20with%20any%20wrongdoing%20for%20his%20Burisma%20service.%20Instead%2C%20Special%20Counsel%20David%20Weiss%20has%20indicted%20Hunter%20for%20tax%20evasion%20and%20lying%20on%20a%20form%20to%20purchase%20a%20firearm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20revelation%20about%20Rollie's%20thumb%20drive%20comes%20shortly%20after%20the%20indictment%20of%20Smirnov%2C%20for%20allegedly%20making%20false%20statements%20about%20Hunter%20Biden%20in%20June%202020.%20Like%20Smirnov%2C%20Rollie's%20materials%20accuse%20Hunter%20Biden%20of%20involving%20his%20father%20in%20Burisma's%20business%20and%20committing%20a%20vast%20off-the-books%20fraud.%20Smirnov's%20alleged%20lies%20included%20the%20allegation%20that%20Burisma%20officials%20paid%20a%20%245%20million%20bribe%20to%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20and%20were%20memorialized%20in%20an%20FBI%20form%201023%2C%20which%20records%20raw%20reporting%20from%20confidential%20sources%2C%20that%20was%20circulated%20by%20GOP%20Sen.%20Charles%20Grassley.%20The%20thumb%20drive%20incident%20raises%20further%20questions%20about%20the%20ease%20with%20which%20foreign%20actors%20can%20obtain%20access%20to%20the%20highest%20levels%20of%20the%20US%20government%20and%20then%20pass%20off%20rubbish%20as%20legitimate%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Pompeo%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20repeated%20requests%20for%20comment.%20There%20is%20no%20evidence%20to%20suggest%20that%20Pompeo%20or%20his%20aide%20did%20anything%20with%20the%20material%20on%20the%20thumb%20drive%20after%20receiving%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20State%20Department%20official%20who%20served%20under%20Pompeo%20told%20BI%20that%20it%20was%20not%20unusual%20for%20officials%20to%20receive%20random%20material%20from%20people%20they%20meet%20at%20social%20events%2C%20and%20that%20there%20was%20a%20process%20in%20place%20for%20handing%20such%20materials%20off%20to%20in-house%20experts%20for%20evaluation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Claremont%20Institute%2C%20which%20was%20responsible%20for%20vetting%20the%20gala%20guest%20list%2C%20on%20Thursday%20and%20did%20not%20immediately%20receive%20a%20reply.%20After%202016%2C%20the%20Claremont%20Institute%20drifted%20from%20traditional%20conservative%20politics%20into%20more%20extreme%20territory.%20It%20granted%20a%20fellowship%20to%20MAGA%20troublemaker%20Jack%20Posobiec%2C%20who%20has%20used%20his%20online%20platform%20to%20spread%20conspiracy%20theories%2C%20and%20served%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Finteractive%2F2024%2F01%2F20%2Fus%2Fdei-woke-claremont-institute.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20organizing%20hub%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20backlash%20to%20DEI%20initiatives%20in%20higher%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%2C%20the%20Justice%20Department%2C%20and%20a%20lawyer%20representing%20Buma%20did%20not%20immediately%20return%20requests%20for%20comment%20sent%20after%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20reporting%20by%20Anastasiia%20Carrier.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-russia-linked-campaign-to-spread-dirt-about-hunter-biden-and-burisma-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708649878000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657273fd7a3c8094d5dadf1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-russia-linked-campaign-to-spread-dirt-about-hunter-biden-and-burisma-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20KGB%20agent%20handed%20off%20a%20thumb%20drive%20with%20disinfo%20about%20Hunter%20Biden%20to%20a%20Trump%20official%20at%20a%20Claremont%20Institute%20gala.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mschwartz%40businessinsider.com%20(Mattathias%20Schwartz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-russia-linked-campaign-to-spread-dirt-about-hunter-biden-and-burisma-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tyler%20Perry%20Halts%20%24800M%20Studio%20Expansion%2C%20Citing%20Concerns%20Over%20OpenAI%E2%80%99s%20Sora%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708649824000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3