nks%20between%20Mexican%20President%20Lopez%20Obrador%2C%20drug%20cartels%2C%20and%20Mexican%20advisers.%20The%20US%20government%20shelved%20the%20inquiry%20due%20to%20little%20interest%20in%20pursuing%20allegations%20against%20a%20top%20ally.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-examined-allegations-of-cartel-ties-to-allies-of-mexicos-president-report%2Farticleshow%2F107926782.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-examined-allegations-of-cartel-ties-to-allies-of-mexicos-president-report%2Famp_articleshow%2F107926782.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-examined-allegations-of-cartel-ties-to-allies-of-mexicos-president-report%2Famp_articleshow%2F107926782.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Private%20US%20Spaceship%20Successfully%20Lands%20On%20Moon%2C%20Transmitting%20Signal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Houston-based%20company%20has%20landed%20America's%20first%20spaceship%20on%20the%20Moon%20in%20more%20than%2050%20years%2C%20part%20of%20a%20new%20fleet%20of%20NASA-funded%2C%20uncrewed%20commercial%20robots%20intended%20to%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20astronaut%20missions%20later%20this%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20flight%20controllers%20confirmed%20they%20had%20received%20a%20faint%20signal%2C%20it%20was%20not%20immediately%20clear%20whether%20Odysseus%2C%20the%20lander%20built%20by%20Intuitive%20Machines%2C%20was%20fully%20functional%2C%20with%20announcers%20on%20a%20live%20stream%20suggesting%20it%20may%20have%20come%20down%20off-kilter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hexagon-shaped%20vessel%20touched%20down%20near%20the%20lunar%20south%20pole%20at%202323%20GMT%2C%20having%20slowed%20from%204%2C000%20miles%20(6%2C500%20kilometers)%20per%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImages%20from%20an%20external%20%26quot%3BEagleCam%26quot%3B%20that%20was%20supposed%20to%20shoot%20out%20from%20the%20spacecraft%20during%20its%20final%20seconds%20of%20descent%20could%20be%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20time%20being%2C%20however%2C%20nothing%20is%20certain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20a%20doubt%20our%20equipment%20is%20on%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20Moon%20and%20we%20are%20transmitting%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tim%20Crain%2C%20the%20company's%20chief%20technology%20officer.%20%26quot%3BSo%20congratulations%20IM%20team%2C%20we'll%20see%20how%20much%20more%20we%20can%20get%20from%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20previous%20moonshot%20by%20another%20American%20company%20last%20month%20ended%20in%20failure%2C%20raising%20the%20stakes%20to%20demonstrate%20that%20private%20industry%20has%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20repeat%20a%20feat%20last%20achieved%20by%20US%20space%20agency%20NASA%20during%20its%20manned%20Apollo%2017%20mission%20in%201972.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20mission%20%26quot%3Bwill%20be%20one%20of%20the%20first%20forays%20into%20the%20south%20pole%20to%20actually%20look%20at%20the%20environmental%20conditions%20to%20a%20place%20we're%20going%20to%20be%20sending%20our%20astronauts%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20senior%20NASA%20official%20Joel%20Kearns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20type%20of%20dust%20or%20dirt%20is%20there%2C%20how%20hot%20or%20cold%20does%20it%20get%2C%20what's%20the%20radiation%20environment%3F%20These%20are%20all%20things%20you'd%20really%20like%20to%20know%20before%20you%20send%20the%20first%20human%20explorers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ELunar%20south%20pole%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOdysseus%20launched%20February%2015%20on%20a%20SpaceX%20Falcon%209%20rocket%20and%20boasts%20a%20new%20type%20of%20supercooled%20liquid%20oxygen%2C%20liquid%20methane%20propulsion%20system%20that%20allowed%20it%20to%20race%20through%20space%20in%20quick%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20landing%20site%2C%20Malapert%20A%2C%20is%20an%20impact%20crater%20300%20kilometers%20(180%20miles)%20from%20the%20lunar%20south%20pole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENASA%20hopes%20to%20eventually%20build%20a%20long-term%20presence%20and%20harvest%20ice%20there%20for%20both%20drinking%20water%20and%20rocket%20fuel%20under%20Artemis%2C%20its%20flagship%20Moon-to-Mars%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstruments%20carried%20on%20Odysseus%20include%20cameras%20to%20investigate%20how%20the%20lunar%20surface%20changes%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20engine%20plume%20from%20a%20spaceship%2C%20and%20a%20device%20to%20analyze%20clouds%20of%20charged%20dust%20particles%20that%20hang%20over%20the%20surface%20at%20twilight%20as%20a%20result%20of%20solar%20radiation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20carries%20a%20NASA%20landing%20system%20that%20fires%20laser%20pulses%2C%20measuring%20the%20time%20taken%20for%20the%20signal%20to%20return%20and%20its%20change%20in%20frequency%20to%20precisely%20judge%20the%20spacecraft's%20velocity%20and%20distance%20from%20the%20surface%2C%20to%20avoid%20a%20catastrophic%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20instrument%20was%20meant%20to%20run%20as%20a%20demonstration%20only%2C%20but%20Odysseus%20eventually%20had%20to%20rely%20on%20it%20for%20the%20entire%20descent%20phase%20of%20its%20journey%2C%20after%20its%20own%20navigation%20system%20stopped%20working%20--%20forcing%20controllers%20to%20upload%20a%20software%20patch%20to%20make%20the%20switch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EExclusive%20club%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20of%20the%20cargo%20was%20paid%20for%20by%20Intuitive%20Machines'%20private%20clients%2C%20and%20includes%20125%20stainless%20steel%20mini%20Moons%20by%20the%20artist%20Jeff%20Koons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20an%20archive%20created%20by%20a%20nonprofit%20whose%20goal%20is%20to%20leave%20backups%20of%20human%20knowledge%20across%20the%20solar%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENASA%20paid%20Intuitive%20Machines%20%24118%20million%20to%20ship%20its%20hardware%20under%20a%20new%20initiative%20called%20Commercial%20Lunar%20Payload%20Services%20(CLPS)%2C%20which%20it%20created%20to%20delegate%20cargo%20services%20to%20the%20private%20sector%20to%20achieve%20savings%20and%20stimulate%20a%20wider%20lunar%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20CLPS%20mission%2C%20by%20Pittsburgh-based%20Astrobotic%2C%20launched%20in%20January%2C%20but%20its%20Peregrine%20spacecraft%20sprung%20a%20fuel%20leak%20and%20was%20eventually%20brought%20back%20to%20burn%20up%20in%20Earth's%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpaceships%20landing%20on%20the%20Moon%20must%20navigate%20treacherous%20boulders%20and%20craters%20and%2C%20absent%20an%20atmosphere%20to%20support%20parachutes%2C%20must%20rely%20on%20thrusters%20to%20control%20their%20descent.%20Roughly%20half%20of%20the%20more%20than%2050%20attempts%20have%20failed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20now%2C%20only%20the%20space%20agencies%20of%20the%20Soviet%20Union%2C%20United%20States%2C%20China%2C%20India%20and%20Japan%20have%20accomplished%20the%20feat%2C%20making%20for%20an%20exclusive%20club.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708649280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fqh7tpu8_odysseus_625x300_22_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fprivate-us-spaceship-successfully-lands-on-moon-transmitting-signal-5110056%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Houston-based%20company%20has%20landed%20America's%20first%20spaceship%20on%20the%20Moon%20in%20more%20than%2050%20years%2C%20part%20of%20a%20new%20fleet%20of%20NASA-funded%2C%20uncrewed%20commercial%20robots%20intended%20to%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20astronaut%20missions%20later%20this%20decade.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canoni