%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20plaintiffs%20say%20Stanley's%20parent%20company%20withheld%20information%20from%20consumers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFranzetti%2C%20who%20purchased%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-stanley-cup-wedding-day-harry-potter-books-quencher-collection-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStanley%20cup%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20%2435%20in%20March%202023%2C%20said%20in%20her%20complaint%20that%20it%20was%20now%20%26quot%3Bessentially%20worthless%26quot%3B%20to%20her%20because%20it%20contained%20%26quot%3Blead%2C%20a%20highly%20toxic%20metal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlaintiff%20can%20no%20longer%20trust%20using%20this%20product%20safely%20for%20fear%20of%20lead%20exposure%20to%20her%20and%20her%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20PMI%20did%20not%20disclose%20that%20the%20company%20used%20materials%20with%20lead%20to%20make%20the%20product%2C%20and%20it%20should%20not%20have%20fallen%20on%20customers%20to%20assume%20the%20%26quot%3Btoxic%20metal%26quot%3B%20was%20in%20the%20company's%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFranzetti%20told%20BI%20on%20Thursday%20that%20she%20would%20not%20have%20bought%20a%20Stanley%20cup%20if%20she%20had%20known%20more%20about%20the%20manufacturing%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stanley%20cups%20for%20sale%20on%20a%20shelf%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65aad2446979d7371824e6e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStanley%20cups%20have%20become%20massively%20popular.%20%3Cp%3EMatt%20Fowler%20KC%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20never%20have%20purchased%20a%20Stanley%20cup%20had%20I%20known%20there%20was%20lead%20inside%2C%20and%20I%20think%20it%20was%20disingenuous%20that%20Stanley%20did%20not%20disclose%20this%20information%20to%20consumers%20from%20t