0told%20his%20coconspirators%20he%20wanted%20to%20%26quot%3Bstuff%20the%20drugs%20up%20the%20noses%20of%20the%20gringos.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%2C%20which%20began%20with%20opening%20statements%20Wednesday%2C%20sheds%20light%20on%20how%20deep%20the%20corruption%20of%20the%20drug%20cartel%20runs%20in%20Honduras%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20that%20corruption%20allows%20cocaine%20to%20end%20up%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20cities%20and%20towns%20in%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArdon%20Soriano%20testified%20Thursday%20that%20he%20gave%20millions%20in%20drug%20money%20to%20Hern%C3%A1ndez%20and%20the%20National%20Party%20over%20the%20years%20and%20assisted%20with%20election%20fraud%20and%20bribing%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoriano%20described%20to%20the%20jury%20on%20Thursday%20a%202013%20meeting%20he%20attended%20with%20El%20Chapo%20in%20Esp%C3%ADritu%2C%20Cop%C3%A1n%2C%20at%20the%20property%20of%20Miguel%20Arnulfo%20Valle%20Valle%20and%20his%20younger%20brother%20Luis%20Alfonso%20%E2%80%94%20two%20of%20the%20most%20notorious%20cocaine%20traffickers%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArdon%20Soriano%20testified%20that%20an%20associate%20of%20El%20Chapo%20had%20told%20him%20to%20bring%20Hern%C3%A1ndez's%20brother%2C%20Tony%2C%20to%20the%20meeting.%20At%20the%20meeting%2C%20El%20Chapo%20told%20Tony%20Hern%C3%A1ndez%20he%20was%20looking%20to%20open%20new%20trafficking%20routes%20through%20Honduras.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETony%20Hern%C3%A1ndez%20said%20that%20if%20his%20brother%20won%20the%20presidential%20election%20%26quot%3Bhe%20could%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20Ardon%20Soriano%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEl%20Chapo%20then%20asked%20if%2C%20under%20his%20brother's%20administration%2C%20the%20Valle%20brothers%20or%20Ardon%20Soriano%20himself%20would%20be%20extradited%20for%20prosecution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTony%20Hern%C3%A1ndez%20said%20that%20if%20Juan%20Orlando%20won%2C%20that%20we%20would%20not%20be%20extradited%2C%26quot%3B%20Ardon%20Soriano%20told%20the%20jury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20point%2C%20El%20Chapo%20offered%20%241%20million%20to%20Hern%C3%A1ndez's%20campaign%2C%20Ardon%20Soriano%20testified.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22940%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22el%20chapo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F55ba4f52371d2211008bb449%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22371%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEl%20Chapo%20was%20convicted%20in%202019%20of%20drug%20trafficking%2C%20money%20laundering%2C%20and%20weapons-related%20offenses.%3Cp%3EUS%20State%20Department%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTony%20Hern%C3%A1ndez%20said%20he%20had%20to%20speak%20with%20his%20brother%20to%20see%20if%20he%20should%20accept%20the%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Ardon%20Soriano%20said%2C%20adding%20later%2C%20%26quot%3BTony%20Hern%C3%A1ndez%20told%20me%20that%20he'd%20spoken%20to%20Juan%20Orlando%20Hern%C3%A1ndez%20and%20that%20they%20needed%20the%20money%20for%20the%20campaign.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20different%20meeting%20that%20year%2C%20Ardon%20Soriano%20and%20Tony%20Hern%C3%A1ndez%20met%20with%20El%20Chapo%20again%2C%20and%20El%20Chapo%20personally%20handed%20the%20briefcase%20with%20%241%20million%20to%20Hern%C3%A1ndez%2C%20the%20convicted%20drug%20trafficker%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHern%C3%A1ndez%20barely%20won%20the%202013%20election%2C%20with%2036.89%25%20of%20the%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20year%2C%20when%20the%20Valle%20brothers%20were%20extradited%20to%20the%20United%20States%20to%20face%20prosecution%20on%20drug%20trafficking%20charges%2C%20El%20Chapo%20and%20his%20associates%20were%20worried%2C%20Ardon%20Soriano%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drug%20lord%20wanted%20to%20know%20if%20Ardon%20and%20others%20were%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20some%20point%20in%202014%20or%202015%2C%20both%20Juan%20Orlando%20and%20Tony%20Hern%C3%A1ndez%20met%20with%20El%20Chapo%20to%20discuss%20the%20extradition%2C%20Ardon%20Soriano%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJuan%20Orlando%20Hern%C3%A1ndez%20told%20me%20that%20he%20had%20had%20them%20extradited%20because%20they%20had%20tried%20to%20have%20him%20killed%2C%26quot%3B%20Ardon%20Soriano%20told%20the%20jury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20then%20got%20angry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJuan%20Orlando%20Hern%C3%A1ndez%20said%20that%20he%20had%20no%20obligation%20to%20anyone%20and%20that%20if%20they%20wanted%20the%20money%20back%2C%20he%20could%20return%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Ardon%20Soriano%20testified%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20president%20then%20stormed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EArdon%20Soriano%20says%20he's%20a%20better%20person%20now%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EArdon%20Soriano's%20testimony%20for%20the%20prosecution%20concluded%20just%20after%20the%20lunch%20break%2C%20and%20he%20spent%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20day%20under%20cross-examination%20by%20defense%20attorney%20Raymond%20Colon%2C%20who%20began%20by%20questioning%20Ardon's%20motive%20for%20testifying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20just%20trying%20to%20tell%20the%20truth%20and%20get%20a%20new%20lease%20on%20life%20as%20a%20better%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20convicted%20drug%20trafficker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20you're%20a%20better%20person%20now%3F%26quot%3B%20Colon%20fired%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20time%20I've%20spent%20in%20jail%20has%20made%20me%20a%20better%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ardon%20Soriano%2C%20who%20has%20been%20in%20custody%20since%20surrendering%20to%20US%20law%20enforcement%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20focusing%20on%20the%20truth%20of%20the%20allegations%20Ardon%20made%20in%20his%20earlier%20testimony%2C%20Colon%20spent%20the%20afternoon%20almost%20exclusively%20on%20Ardon's%20violent%20past%2C%20including%20his%20direct%20involvement%20over%20the%20years%20in%20dozens%20of%20murders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20list%20some%20of%20the%20names%20of%20the%2056%20you've%20killed%20or%20had%20killed%2C%20and%20I%20want%20you%20to%20tell%20me%20if%20it%20was%20personal%2C%20revenge%2C%20or%20related%20to%20drug%20trafficking%2C%26quot%3B%20Colon%20said%2C%20as%20he%20launched%20into%20questions%20about%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20murders%20spanning%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Colon's%20point%20soon%20got%20badly%20muddled%20by%20his%20meandering%20and%20poorly%20worded%20questions%20that%20frequently%20misstated%20facts%2C%20dates%2C%20and%20names%2C%20raising%20numerous%20objections%20from%20both%20the%20prosecution%20and%20Judge%20Kevin%20Castel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArdon%20Soriano%20grew%20testy%20at%20times%20as%20he%20gave%20answers%20to%20questions%20about%20events%20already%20covered%20at%20length.%20And%20on%20the%20beach%2C%20Castel%20began%20to%20lose%20patience%2C%20even%20snapping%20at%20Colon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20only%20three%20questions%20ago%2C%20please!%26quot%3B%20Castel%20said%20after%20reading%20back%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20transcript%20to%20help%20Colon%20return%20to%20his%20place%20in%20the%20questioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20afternoon%20drew%20to%20a%20close%2C%20Colon%20asked%20a%20final%20question%20about%20one%20of%20Ardon's%20murders%2C%20seemingly%20unaware%20that%20Ardon%20had%20walked%20him%20through%20that%20incident%20hours%20earlier%20at%20the%20very%20start%20of%20cross-examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20defense%20table%2C%20Hern%C3%A1ndez%20could%20be%20seen%20at%20one%20point%20pinching%20the%20bridge%20of%20his%20nose%20and%20scrunching%20his%20eyes%20shut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20is%20scheduled%20to%20resume%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fel-chapo-gave-1-million-campaign-honduras-president-hernandez-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708637676000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d7b67fce7f1785b2e342f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bus