www.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-68372050.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sharad%20Pawar's%20Party%20Allotted%20New%20Poll%20Symbol%20By%20Election%20Commission%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20the%20Election%20Commission%20awarded%20the%20NCP%20name%20and%20'clock'%20symbol%20to%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%2C%20a%20new%20symbol%20has%20been%20allotted%20to%20the%20camp%20led%20by%20the%20party's%20founder%20Sharad%20Pawar.%20The%20symbol%20given%20to%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(Shardchandra%20Pawar)%20is%20called%20'man%20blowing%20turha'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'turha'%20is%20a%20traditional%20trumpet%20and%20is%20also%20known%20as%20'tutari'.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Tutari%20in%20the%20form%20of%20great%20valour%20of%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20had%20once%20deafened%20the%20emperor%20of%20Delhi.%20It%20is%20a%20great%20honour%20for%20our%20party%20to%20get%20Tutari%20(Man%20Blowing%20Turha)%20as%20our%20symbol%20for%20upcoming%20elections.%20Our%20Tutari%20is%20now%20ready%20to%20shake%20Delhi's%20throne%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Sharadchandra%20Pawar%2C%26quot%3B%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission's%20order%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20faction%20had%20been%20given%20on%20February%206%20and%2C%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20said%20that%20the%20name%20given%20to%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20camp%20would%20continue%20till%20further%20orders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHearing%20a%20petition%20by%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20camp%20against%20the%20February%206%20order%2C%20the%20bench%20had%20given%20the%20NCP%20founder%20liberty%20to%20approach%20the%20Election%20Commission%20for%20the%20symbol.%20It%20had%20also%20directed%20the%20poll%20panel%20to%20allot%20the%20symbol%20within%20a%20week%20of%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20group%20applying%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppearing%20for%20the%20NCP%20founder%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%20had%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20name%20allotted%20to%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20was%20an%20interim%20arrangement%20made%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20till%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20which%20will%20be%20held%20on%20February%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20budget%20session%20of%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20is%20scheduled%20to%20start%20from%20February%2026%20and%20our%20group%20will%20be%20without%20any%20name%20or%20symbol%20after%20February%2027.%20The%20order%20said%20that%20Ajit%20Pawar%20side%20is%20the%20real%20NCP%2C%20which%20we%20will%20contest%20at%20a%20later%20stage.%20But%20for%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20can%20use%20the%20name%20as%20a%20one-time%20measure.%20After%20February%2027%2C%20technically%20I%20will%20be%20nameless%2C%20symbol-less%20and%20will%20be%20bound%20to%20obey%20the%20whip%20of%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singhvi%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllotting%20the%20symbol%20to%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20camp%20on%20Thursday%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Commission%20has%20already%20allotted%20the%20name%20of%20'Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20-%20Sharadchandra%20Pawar'%20to%20the%20group%20led%20by%20Sh.%20Sharad%20Pawar%20(respondent)%20as%20per%20the%20Commission's%20Final%20Order%20dated%2006.02.2024%20in%20Dispute%20Case%20No.%202%20of%202023%2C%20till%20further%20orders%20by%20Hon'ble%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20matter.%20Further%2C%20as%20per%20the%20request%20received%2C%20'Man%20Blowing%20Turha'%20is%20allotted%20to%20the%20group%2Fparty%20in%20all%20the%20parliamentary%20constituencies%20in%20the%20State%20of%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20huge%20jolt%20to%20his%20uncle%20and%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%20had%20split%20the%20NCP%20in%20July%202023%20and%20taken%20oath%20as%20a%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20in%20the%20Eknath%20Sh