posure%20to%20freezing%20temperatures%2C%20which%20significantly%20contributed%20to%20his%20death.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20student%20was%20f%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fparents-of-dead-indian-american-student-accuse-police-of-negligence-4941722%5C%22%3Eound%20dead%20on%20January%2020%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20his%20body%20was%20found%20on%20the%20back%20porch%20of%20a%20building%20near%20the%20university%20campus%20in%20west%20Urbana%20in%20the%20US%20state%20of%20Illinois.%20There%20were%20signs%20of%20hypothermia%20when%20his%20body%20was%20found%20but%20the%20exact%20cause%20of%20death%20was%20under%20investigation%20by%20the%20campus%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Denied%20Entry%20In%20Club'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkul%20was%20out%20for%20drinks%20with%20friends%20on%20January%2020.%20Around%2011%3A30%20at%20night%2C%20he%20and%20his%20friends%20decided%20to%20go%20to%20the%20Canopy%20Club%20-%20a%20venue%20close%20to%20the%20campus%20that%20they%20had%20visited%20before%20that%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20staff%20at%20the%20club%20denied%20him%20entry.%20He%20tried%20to%20enter%20the%20club%20%26quot%3Bmultiple%20times%26quot%3B%20but%20was%20repeatedly%20denied%20by%20staff%2C%26quot%3B%20investigators%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20also%20turned%20down%20two%20rideshare%20vehicles%20called%20for%20him%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kansascity.com%2Fnews%2Fnation-world%2Fnational%2Farticle285736931.html%5C%22%3EKansas%20City%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIllinois%20and%20much%20of%20the%20midwest%20experienced%20brutal%20cold%20and%20freezing%20temperatures%20in%20the%20latter%20half%20of%20January%2C%20with%20wind%20chills%20dipping%20between%20-20%20to%20-30%20degrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20calls%20were%20made%20to%20him%20that%20went%20unanswered%20and%20a%20friend%20contacted%20the%20campus%20police%20to%20search%20him.%20According%20to%20police%2C%20an%20officer%20looked%20for%20Dhawan%20by%20driving%20%26quot%3Bat%20a%20walking%20pace%26quot%3B%20near%20the%20%26quot%3Blikely%20path%26quot%3B%20he%20would%20have%20taken%20back%20to%20campus%20but%20did%20not%20see%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20morning%2C%20an%20employee%20of%20the%20university%20notified%20police%20and%20emergency%20medical%20services%20of%20%26quot%3Ba%20man%20on%20the%20back%20porch%20of%20a%20building%26quot%3B.%20Police%20said%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bdead%20at%20the%20time%20he%20was%20found%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkul's%20parents%20-%20Ish%20and%20Ritu%20Dhawan%20said%20their%20son%20was%20found%20just%20400%20feet%20from%20where%20he%20was%20reported%20missing%20based%20on%20location-tracking%20data%20on%20their%20son's%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhawan%2C%20who%20turned%2018%20in%20September%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20The%20News-Gazette%2C%20came%20to%20the%20University%20of%20Illinois'%20Department%20of%20Electrical%20and%20Computer%20Engineering%20to%20study%20robotics%20despite%20his%20parent's%20opposition%2C%20who%20wished%20him%20to%20be%20closer%20to%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Jaahnavi%20Kandula%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20year%20of%20legal%20battles%2C%20court%20proceedings%2C%20and%20calls%20for%20accountability%2C%20the%20police%20officer%20who%20was%20accused%20of%20running%20his%20vehicle%20over%20Jaajnavi%20Kandula%20will%20walk%20free.%20She%20was%C2%A0a%2023-year-old%20Indian%20student%2C%20who%20was%20killed%20after%20being%20hit%20by%20a%20speeding%20police%20vehicle%20in%20the%20US%20state%20of%20Washington%20on%20January%2023%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20acknowledging%20the%20impact%20on%20communities%20both%20locally%20and%20%26quot%3Bacross%20the%20world%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20US%20prosecutor%20claimed%20a%20lack%20of%20%26quot%3Bsufficient%20evidence%26quot%3B%20to%20pursue%20criminal%20charges%20against%20Seattle%20police%20office