back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20will%20shoot%20if%20I%20go%20to%20the%20high%20canal%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mr%20Brajarala%2C%20who%20will%20wait%20for%20the%20cows%20to%20return%20on%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20they%20don't%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20do%20anything%2C%20can't%20walk%20there%20and%20bring%20them%2C%20though%20we%20have%20lost%20many%20cows%20since%20May%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20month%20in%202023%20when%20ethnic%20clashes%20broke%20out%20between%20the%20hill-majority%20Kuki-Zo%20tribes%20and%20the%20valley-majority%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F3s5mdq0g_naranseina-manipur_625x300_22_February_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Brajarala%2C%2060%2C%20lives%20alone%20in%20a%20hut%20in%20the%20village%2022%20km%20from%20the%20Kuki-Zo-dominated%20Churachandpur%20district%2C%20which%20comes%20under%20the%20%26quot%3Bhill%20area%26quot%3B%20category%20of%20Manipur's%20complex%20land%20laws.%20The%20hill%20ranges%20that%20touch%20Churachandpur%20go%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20opposite%20direction%20of%20the%20valley%2C%20and%20Mr%20Brajarala's%20home%20is%20in%20one%20of%20the%20villages%20in%20the%20foothills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmer%2C%20in%20a%20red%20t-shirt%20and%20a%20camouflage%20hat%2C%20a%20mud-soaked%20spade%20in%20his%20hand%2C%20points%20towards%20his%20village%20behind%20the%20%26quot%3Blow%20canal%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20bullets%20have%20reached%20there.%20They%20came%20down%20from%20the%20hills%20and%20fired%2C%20we%20all%20saw%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeavy%20gunfights%20broke%20out%20between%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki-Zo%20armed%20groups%20in%20August%20and%20September%202023.%20Both%20sides%20call%20themselves%20%26quot%3Bvillage%20defence%20volunteers%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20definition%20of%20the%20belligerents%20in%20Manipur%20that%20has%20become%20the%20most%20controversial%20since%20nothing%20stops%20these%20%26quot%3Bvolunteers%26quot%3B%20from%20killing%20people%20under%20the%20insurance%20provided%20by%20%26quot%3Bin%20self-defence%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20central%20forces%20are%20at%20the%20high%20canal%20area%2C%20which%20they%20call%20a%20buffer%20zone.%20But%20we%20can't%20harvest%20anything%20beyond%20the%20high%20canal%20because%20every%20time%20we%20go%20there%2C%20they%20start%20shooting%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Brajarala%20says.%20%26quot%3BWe%20spoke%20with%20the%20central%20forces.%20They%20asked%20us%20to%20wait%20for%20things%20to%20calm%20down%20a%20bit%20since%20tension%20is%20very%20high.%20But%20it%20has%20been%20nine%20months.%20How%20long%20do%20we%20have%20to%20wait%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20one%20night%20in%20November%20he%20walked%20up%20to%20the%20high%20canal%20and%20met%20a%20central%20force%20officer%20to%20demand%20where's%20the%20gunfire%20coming%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20asked%20him%2C%20'show%20me%20till%20where%20I%20can%20go'.%20The%20officer%20told%20me%2C%20pointing%20at%20my%20feet%2C%20'only%20till%20here'%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mr%20Brajarala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fqc0273p_naranseina-manipur_625x300_22_February_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20farmer%20in%20Naranseina%2C%20Salam%20Phulen%2C%20says%20they%20could%20not%20harvest%2060%20hectares%20of%20paddy%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20high%20canal%20near%20the%20hills.%20This%20village%20in%20Bishnupur%20district%20is%20only%206%20km%20from%20Moirang%20town%2C%20known%20for%20the%2