of%20the%20SKM%2C%20told%20the%20media%20during%20a%20press%20conference%20that%20these%20groups%20decided%20to%20march%20for%20Delhi%20without%20consulting%20the%20SKM.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20join%20them%20now%2C%20it%20would%20give%20the%20impression%20that%20we%20are%20going%20there%20to%20disturb%20their%20programme%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rajewal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20why%20SKM%20was%20not%20showing%20unity%2C%20Rajewal%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20media%20should%20not%20put%20their%20words%20on%20our%20mouth.%20Our%20focus%20is%20on%20unity%20and%20the%20welfare%20of%20all%20farmers.%20Despite%20the%20separation%20of%20the%20Dallewal%20and%20Pandher%20groups%20from%20the%20SKM%2C%20we%20have%20still%20formed%20a%20six-member%20committee%20to%20establish%20coordination%20with%20them%20and%20advance%20our%20common%20demands%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajewal%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20on%20whether%20protesting%20farmers%20should%20march%20ahead%20or%20call%20off%20their%20protest%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20strong%20police%20action%20is%20for%20them%20to%20make%2C%20as%20they%20are%20managing%20the%20entire%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESKM%E2%80%99s%20decision%20came%20a%20day%20after%20Dallewal%20invited%20all%20farm%20unions%20to%20bolster%20their%20protest%20at%20the%20borders%2C%20following%20the%20death%20of%20a%20farmer%20at%20the%20Khanauri%20border%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20situation%20is%20calm%20at%20the%20borders%20since%20their%20Delhi%20march%20remains%20suspended%20till%20Friday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandher%20told%20the%20media%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20Thursday%20that%20they%20would%20announce%20their%20next%20course%20of%20action%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESKM%20announces%20nationwide%20protest%20in%20response%20to%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20death%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESKM%2C%20in%20response%20to%20the%20death%20of%2022-year-old%20farmer%20Shubkaran%20Singh%20