s%20happening%20in%20court%20and%20what%20was%20happening%20in%20Dolton.%20And%20they%20told%20me%20they%20were%20investigating%20and%20would%20be%20in%20touch%20with%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20he%20had%20been%20interviewed%20by%20the%20FBI%20along%20with%20five%20others%20who%20range%20from%20a%20public%20official%2C%20business%20owners%20and%20a%20former%20village%20employee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInquiries%20are%20being%20made%20by%20agents%20over%20Ms%20Henyard's%20purported%20use%20of%20public%20funds%20and%20resources%2C%20which%20includes%20extravagant%20out-of-town%20travel%20expenses.%20Investigations%20have%20also%20been%20done%20over%20Ms%20Henyard's%20purported%20exploitation%20of%20public%20employees%20and%20tax%20dollars%20for%20personal%20gain%2C%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20in%20police%20overtime%20for%20her%20personal%20security%20detail%2C%20and%20the%20delaying%20of%20licenses%20to%20specific%20businesses%2C%20as%20per%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDolton%20Trustee%20Jason%20House%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Board%20of%20Trustees%20and%20I%20have%20repeatedly%20questioned%20the%20Mayor's%20Office%20on%20her%20use%20of%20public%20funds.%20We%20welcome%20any%20investigation%20that%20will%20bring%20transparency%20on%20how%20taxpayer%20dollars%20are%20being%20spent.%20Our%20residents%20deserve%20this%20level%20of%20financial%20transparency.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20public%20relations%20firm%2C%20on%20behalf%20of%20Ms%20Henyard%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMayor%20Tiffany%20Henyard%20and%20the%20Village%20of%20Dolton%20have%20not%20received%20any%20subpoenas%20and%20have%20not%20been%20contacted%20by%20the%20FBI%20or%20any%20other%20law%20enforcement%20agency.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20after%20the%20Illinois%20Attorney%20General's%20Office%20ordered%20a%20charity%20run%20by%20the%20Dolton%20Mayor%20to%20stop%20soliciting%20d