%20them%20return%20to%20India.%20A%20similar%20appeal%20has%20been%20made%20by%20AIMIM%20MP%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20and%20a%20Karnataka%20minister%20has%20said%20the%20state%20government%20will%20talk%20to%20the%20MEA%20about%20getting%20the%20men%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFamily%20members%20of%20the%20youngsters%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20one%20of%20them%2C%20Syed%20Ilyas%20from%20Hyderabad%2C%20had%20sent%20a%20video%20from%20Russia%20telling%20his%20parents%20that%20he%20and%20several%20others%20had%20been%20cheated%20by%20the%20agent.%20In%20the%20video%2C%20Mr%20Ilyas%20said%20he%20had%20not%20signed%20up%20to%20fight%20the%20war%20and%20pleaded%20with%20his%20family%20to%20be%20brought%20back%20to%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20of%20one%20of%20the%20young%20men%20said%20at%20least%2010-12%20Indians%20-%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20other%20states%20-%20have%20been%20duped%20this%20way%20and%20one%20of%20them%2C%20who%20is%20from%20Kashmir%2C%20was%20injured%20after%20he%20suffered%20a%20bullet%20injury%20to%20his%20leg.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20son%2C%20Abdul%20Naeem%2C%20and%20three%20of%20his%20friends%20used%20to%20work%20in%20Dubai.%20They%20got%20in%20touch%20with%20an%20agent%20called%20Baba%20who%20promised%20them%20high-paying%20security%20jobs%20in%20Russia%20and%20took%20Rs%203%20lakh%20each%20from%20them.%20They%20were%20brought%20back%20to%20India%20and%20then%20sent%20to%20Russia%20on%20December%2016.%20They%20were%20told%20to%20sign%20an%20agreement%20in%20Russian%2C%20but%20they%20refused%2C%20and%20relented%20only%20when%20the%20agent%20told%20them%20it%20was%20safe%20and%20about%20their%20security%20guard%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Naeem's%20father%20said%20in%20Hindi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20least%2010-12%20young%20men%20have%20been%20duped%20this%20way.%20My%20son%20and%20all%20the%20others%20want%20to%20come%20back.%20We%20have%20no%20complaints%20with%20the%20Russian%20government%20or%20their%20army%2C%20we%20are%20requesting%20them%20to%20send%20our%20sons%20back.%20We%20are%20also%20appealing%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20ensure%20their%20safe%20return%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20added%20that%20he%20is%20in%20touch%20with%20his%20son%2C%20who%20is%20now%20being%20kept%20apart%20from%20his%20three%20friends.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20being%20taken%20in%20planes%20to%20places%20far%20away.%20A%20man%20from%20Kashmir%20has%20also%20suffered%20a%20bullet%20injury%20to%20his%20leg%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInjured%20During%20Fighting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20family%20from%20Kasganj%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20is%20also%20undergoing%20a%20similar%20ordeal%20after%20being%20cheated%20by%20the%20same%20agent.%20A%20young%20man%20was%20taken%20to%20Russia%20and%20promised%20a%20job%20as%20a%20labourer%2C%20but%20ended%20up%20fighting%20the%20Ukrainian%20army%20for%20over%20two%20months.%20He%20has%20finally%20managed%20to%20contact%20his%20family%20from%20a%20hospital%20after%20he%20was%20injured%20in%20the%20fighting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERequesting%20anonymity%2C%20the%20man's%20father%20said%20the%20agent%2C%20Baba%2C%20ran%20a%20YouTube%20channel%20called%20'Baba%20Vlogs'%20and%20cheated%20people%20by%20promising%20them%20high-paying%20jobs%20in%20Russia.%20After%20the%20man%20was%20offered%20a%20job%20as%20a%20helper%2C%20the%20family%20took%20a%20loan%20to%20pay%20a%20sum%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh%20that%20was%20demanded%20by%20the%20agent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20son%20was%20taken%20to%20Moscow%20on%20November%2011%2C%202023%2C%20along%20with%20two%20young%20men%20from%20Hyderabad%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20He%20was%20asked%20to%20sign%20up%20to%20fight%20the%20war%20and%2C%20when%20he%20refused%2C%20his%20passport%20and%20visa%20were%20taken%20away%20and%20he%20was%20made%20to%20sign%20an%20agreement%20in%20Russian%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20father%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20hear%20from%20him%20for%20over%20two%20months%20and%20then%20he%20called%20to%20say%20he%20has%20been%20injured.%20We%20haven't%20been%20able%20to%20get%20in%20touch%20with%20him%20since.%20I%20am%20begging%20the%20central%20government%20to%20get%20him%20back.%20I%20had%20taken%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh%20to%20send%20him%20to%20Russia%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20has%20also%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20police%20in%20Kasganj.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Will%20Talk%20To%20MEA'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Minister%20Priyank%20Kharge%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20district%20administration%20has%20alerted%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20MEA.%20We%20will%20talk%20to%20the%20MEA%20and%20do%20our%20best%20to%20bring%20back%20the%20young%20men.%20Not%20only%20the%20men%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20but%20everyone%20who%20has%20been%20duped%20into%20waging%20this%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Mr%20Owaisi%20said%20he%20had%20written%20to%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishnakar%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fduped-by-agent-indians-forced-to-fight-in-russian-war-claims-asaduddin-owaisi-5100448%5C%22%3Esought%20his%20help%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20getting%20the%20young%20men%20back%20to%20India.%20The%20MP%20has%20said%20at%20least%20a%20dozen%20Indians%2C%20including%20three%20from%20Telangana%2C%20had%20been%20duped%20by%20the%20agent%20and%20forced%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20war.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708618740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Ft1pbc4jo_wagner-group-reuters-650_625x300_24_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findians-duped-into-fighting-for-russia-families-appeal-for-safe-return-5107478%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sent%20to%20Russia%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20getting%20good%20salaries%20as%20security%20guards%20or%20labourers%2C%20at%20least%2010%20young%20men%20from%20various%20parts%20of%20India%20are%20now%20being%20forced%20to%20risk%20their%20lives%20and%20fight%20a%20war%20for%20a%20country%20they%20owe%20no%20allegiance%20to.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findians-duped-into-fighting-for-russia-families-appeal-for-safe-return-5107478%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findians-duped-into-fighting-for-russia-families-appeal-for-safe-return-5107478%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findians-duped-into-fighting-for-russia-families-appeal-for-safe-return-5107478%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDifferent%20Rules%3F%26quot%3B%20Ex%20India%20Star%20Blasts%20Those%20Missing%20First-Class%20Cricket%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20talking%20points%20in%20Indian%20cricket%20these%20days%20is%20players%20missing%20domestic%20cricket.%20BCCI%20Secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20recenty%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20all%20centrally%20contracted%20cricketers%2C%20who%20are%20not%20with%20the%20national%20team%2C%20will%20have%20to%20mandatorily%20play%20red-ball%20cricket%20in%20the%20domestic%20circuit%20and%20the%20management%20will%20not%20tolerate%20any%20kind%20of%20excuses%20in%20the%20matter.%20The%20statement%20came%20amidst%20the%20controversy%20surrounding%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ishan%20Kishan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107047-ishan-kishan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIshan%20Kishan%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20reports%20that%20suggest%20that%20BCCI%20has%20asked%20him%20to%20play%20for%20Jharkhand%20in%20Ranji%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20mentioned%20Kishan%20during%20the%20interaction%20but%20quickly%20added%20that%20the%20announcement%20was%20not%20targeted%20towards%20him%20and%20this%20rule%20will%20apply%20for%20all%20cricketers%20who%20are%20not%20part%20of%20the%20national%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20contracted%20players%20have%20been%20told%20on%20phone%20and%20I'll%20be%20writing%20to%20them%20too.%20If%20chairman%20of%20selectors%2C%20coach%20%26amp%3B%20captain%20want%20you%20to%20play%20red-ball%20cricket%20then%20you%20gotta%20play.%20%E2%80%98Nakhre%20Nahi%20Chalenge'%20(no%20tantrums).%20And%20as%20far%20as%20Ishan%20Kishan%20is%20concerned%2C%20he%20is%20young%2C%20I%20am%20not%20saying%20this%20specifically%20about%20him%20as%20it%20will%20be%20applicable%20for%20all%20the%20players%20uniformly%2C%26quot%3B%20Jay%20Shah%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20will%20have%20to%20play%2C%20otherwise%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20selection%20committee%20has%20given%20me%20his%20suggestions%20and%20I%20am%20going%20to%20give%20him%20a%20free%20hand%20to%20let%20him%20take%20his%20own%20calls%20freely.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20midst%20of%20this%2C%20on%20Thursday%20came%20a%20report%20by%20Indian%20Express%20about%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64384-shreyas-santosh-iyer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fa%3E%20making%20himself%20unavailable%20for%20Mumbai's%20Ranji%20Trophy%20quarterfinals%20citing%20injury%20concerns%20but%20the%20National%20Cricket%20Academy%20(NCA)%20has%20said%20that%20he%20has%20no%20'fresh%20injuries'.%20The%20report%20cited%20an%20email%20from%20Nitin%20Patel%2C%20the%20head%20of%20sports%20science%20and%20medicine%20at%20the%20NCA%2C%20who%20told%20selectors%20that%20Iyer%20was%20'fit'.%20It%20also%20quoted%20Mumbai%20Cricket%20Association%20sources%20saying%20that%20Iyer%20had%20cited%20back%20pain%20as%20the%20reason%20behind%20missing%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20quarterfinal%20match%20against%20Baroda%20which%20will%20begin%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShreyas%20Iyer%20was%20fit%20and%20available%20for%20selection%20as%20per%20the%20handover%20report%20of%20the%20Indian%20team%20after%20the%202nd%20Test%20match%20against%20England.%20There%20are%20currently%20no%20fresh%20injuries%20reported%20as%20well%20after%20his%20departure%20from%20Team%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20Patel%20wrote%20in%20his%20email%20according%20to%20the%20report.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Irfan%20Pathan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F607-irfan-pathan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIrfan%20Pathan%3C%2Fa%3E%20posted%20an%20intersting%20comment%20on%20X%20on%20Thursday.%20%26quot%3BIs%20there%20a%20different%20rules%20for%20different%20players%20for%20not%20playing%20Indian%20first%20class%20cricket%20in%20the%20name%20of%20looking%20after%20the%20body%3F%26quot%3B%20Irfan%20Pathan%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIs%20there%20a%20different%20rules%20for%20different%20players%20for%20not%20playing%20Indian%20first%20class%20cricket%20in%20the%20name%20of%20looking%20after%20the%20body%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Irfan%20Pathan%20(%40IrfanPathan)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIrfanPathan%2Fstatus%2F1760668804752003129%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708618320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fnkbcbd0o_ishan-kishan-shreyas-iyer_625x300_17_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fdifferent-rules-ex-india-star-blasts-those-missing-first-class-cricket-in-the-name-of-looking-after-body-5108304%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BCCI%20Secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20recenty%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20all%20centrally%20contracted%20cricketers%2C%20who%20are%20not%20with%20the%20national%20team%2C%20will%20have%20to%20mandatorily%20play%20red-ball%20cricket%20in%20the%20domestic%20circuit%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'They%20will%20do%20something%20with%20my%20son's%20body'%3A%20Navalny's%20mother%20accuses%20Russia%20of%20threats%20over%20burial%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708618320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F1600x900%2Fskynews-lyudmila-navalnaya_6465461.jpg%3F20240222164005%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Falexei-navalnys-mother-sees-sons-body-and-accuses-russia-of-forcing-secret-funeral-without-mourners-13078434%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alexei%20Navalny's%20mother%20has%20said%20she%20has%20seen%20the%20body%20of%20her%20son%20-%20and%20that%20officials%20are%20trying%20to%20force%20her%20to%20hold%20a%20private%20burial%20ceremony%20without%20mourners.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A180%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Falexei-navalnys-mother-sees-sons-body-and-accuses-russia-of-forcing-secret-funeral-without-mourners-13078434%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Falexei-navalnys-mother-sees-sons-body-and-accuses-russia-of-forcing-secret-funeral-without-mourners-13078434%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Falexei-navalnys-mother-sees-sons-body-and-accuses-russia-of-forcing-secret-funeral-without-mourners-13078434%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Grasim%20forays%20into%20paints%20industry%2C%20targets%20Rs%2010%2C000%20cr%20revenue%20in%203%20years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708618103000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-03%2F24%2Ffull%2F1616569960-3988.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business