0less%20than%20what%20their%20UP%20and%20Bihar%20counterparts%20get.%20They%20said%20the%20poor%20living%20condition%20in%20the%20hostel%20compounded%20their%20misery.%20Junior%20female%20doctors%20claimed%20that%20rats%20roam%20around%20the%20hostel%20and%20five%20people%20have%20to%20live%20in%20one%20room%20and%20water%20is%20dripping%20from%20the%20ceiling%20of%20rooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20claimed%20that%20the%20infrastructure%20is%20so%20poor%20that%20sometimes%20they%20have%20to%20sleep%20on%20beds%20assigned%20to%20patients.%20Maharashtra%20is%20reportedly%20the%20richest%20state%20in%20India%20as%20per%20GDP.%20The%20indefinite%20strike%20has%20raised%20concern%20that%20patients%20would%20be%20suffering%20because%20of%20the%20unavailability%20of%20doctors.%20However%2C%20they%20will%20continue%20to%20provide%20emergency%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20want%20to%20cause%20any%20trouble%20to%20the%20patients%2C%20but%20we%20are%20forced%20to%20do%20this.%20We%20have%20been%20raising%20our%20demands%20for%20a%20year.%20There%20are%20more%20doctors%20and%20less%20hostel%20rooms%20for%20them.%20The%20stipend%20is%20less%20than%20Bihar-UP-Delhi%20and%20sometimes%20there's%20a%20delay%20of%20four%20months.%20The%20government%20is%20saying%20they%20will%20credit%20it%20in%20two%20days%2C%20but%20two%20weeks%20have%20passed%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Abhijeet%20Helge%2C%20President%20of%20Maharashtra%20Association%20of%20Resident%20Doctors%20Central%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20the%20distressing%20situation%20of%20resident%20doctors%2C%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20doubt%20was%20always%20given%20to%20the%20authority%2C%20and%20we%20entrusted%20them%20to%20do%20the%20right%20thing%20promptly%20to%20ensure%20the%20welfare%20of%20Resident%20doctors.%20However%2C%20regardless%20of%20our%20innumerable%20pleas%2C%20it%20seems%20our%20genuine%20concerns%20have%20fallen%20on%20deaf%20ears.%20Having%20been%20pushed%20to%