20two%20months.%20The%20star%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20player%20took%20a%20break%20from%20cricket%20and%20returned%20home%20from%20India%20Tour%20of%20South%20Africa.%20Since%20then%2C%20Ishan%20Kishan%20has%20been%20missing%20from%20action.%20In%C2%A0%20this%20period%2C%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E%20mentioned%20that%20Ishan%20Kishan%20has%20to%20play%20some%20form%20of%20the%20game%20to%20make%20a%20return%20to%20the%20Indian%20team.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20BCCI%20has%20also%20made%20it%20mandatory%20for%20centrally%20contracted%20to%20play%20red-ball%20cricket%20in%20the%20domestic%20circuit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%2C%20Ishan%20Kishan%20missed%20his%20state%20Jharkhand's%20last%20Ranji%20Trophy%20game%20this%20season.%20Now%2C%20in%20a%20video%20that%20has%20gone%20viral%2C%20Ishan%20Kishan%20can%20be%20seen%20training%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20authenticity%20of%20the%20video%20cannot%20be%20verified%20by%20NDTV.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIshan%20Kishan%20in%20the%20gym%20session%20with%20Hardik%20Pandya.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FTN3HgEGJrN%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FTN3HgEGJrN%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Mufaddal%20Vohra%20(%40mufaddal_vohra)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmufaddal_vohra%2Fstatus%2F1760671487344926894%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBCCI%20Secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20made%20it%20clear%20on%20Wednesday