ual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fouvngbv8_pandya-ishan_625x300_22_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fishan-kishans-gym-session-video-with-hardik-pandya-viral-amid-row-over-missing-domestic-cricket-tournaments-5107901%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ishan%20Kishan%20took%20a%20break%20from%20cricket%20and%20returned%20home%20from%20India%20Tour%20of%20South%20Africa.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20star%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20player%20has%20been%20missing%20from%20action.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russian%20Skier%20Killed%2C%20Six%20Others%20Rescued%20After%20Avalanche%20in%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Gulmarg%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17121316%2Fimad-clicks-Dg6tMlfSOQ4-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20Russian%20skier%20was%20killed%20while%20six%20others%20were%20rescued%20on%20Thursday%20(February%2022)%20when%20an%20avalanche%20struck%20Mt%20Afarwat%20in%20the%20upper%20reaches%20of%20north%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Gulmarg%20ski%20resort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20officials%2C%20seven%20skiers%20from%20Russia%20had%20planned%20a%20routine%20adventure%20run%20in%20Khilanmarg%20area%20of%20Gulmarg%20when%20an%20avalanche%20struck%20the%20area%20on%20Thursday%20afternoon%2C%20burying%20all%20of%20them%20along%20with%20a%20local%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20area%20is%20prone%20to%20avalanches%2C%20and%20skiers%20go%20there%20on%20their%20own%20risk%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20news%20of%20the%20tragedy%20reached%20the%20Gulmarg%20Ski%20Patrol%2C%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20managing%20sports%20activities%20on%20the%20slopes%20of%20the%20north%20Kashmir%20ski%20resort%2C%20a%20rescue%20team%20was%20rushed%20to%20the%20area%20and%20helicopters%20were%20also%20deployed%20to%20help%20in%20the%20search%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20collaborative%20effort%20between%20the%20Gulmarg%20Ski%20Patrol%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20and%20other%20state%20agencies%20resulted%20in%20the%20successful%20rescue%20of%20the%20group%20as%20well%20as%20one%20local%20guide%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20official%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20slain%20skier%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Hanten%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Moscow.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20body%20has%20been%20taken%20to%20the%20Tangmarg%20sub-district%20hospital%20for%20post-mortem%2C%E2%80%9D%20PTI%20quoted%20a%20local%20police%20officer%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Embassy%20of%20Russia%20in%20India%20maintains%20constant%20contact%20with%20the%20local%20authorities.%20The%20avalanche%20was%20triggered%20by%20the%20heavy%20snowfall%20observed%20in%20the%20region%20since%20February%2017.%20On%20February%2021%2C%20a%20medium%20danger%20level%20avalanche%20warning%20was%20issued%20for%20Baramulla%20district%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20Russian%20embassy%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20from%20the%20scene%20of%20a%20slope%20on%20Mt%20Afarwat%2C%20which%20was%20hit%20by%20the%20avalanche%2C%20showed%20a%20private%20chopper%20landing%20near%20tall%20mounds%20of%20snow.%20The%20local%20guide%20remained%20missing%20for%20some%20time%20but%20he%20was%20rescued%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fourth%20edition%20of%20Khelo%20India%20Games%20or%20National%20Winter%20Games%2C%20which%20were%20inaugurated%C2%A0%20in%20Gulmarg%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20were%20not%20affected%20by%20the%20avalanche%2C%20officials%20said.%20The%20games%20are%20expected%20to%20continue%20till%20February%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20chief%20minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20was%20also%20in%20Gulmarg%20when%20the%20tragedy%20happened%20and%20he%20posted%20about%20the%20incident%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20appears%20the%20skiers%20were%20skiing%20off%20the%20piste%20or%20groomed%20slopes%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98back%20country%E2%80%99.%20Days%20like%20today%20remind%20us%20that%20while%20the%20skiing%20is%20fun%2C%20the%20fresh%20powder%20exhilarating%20%26amp%3B%20the%20visuals%20spectacular%2C%20skiing%20is%20not%20without%20its%20dangers%20%26amp%3B%20risk%20to%20lives.%20Praying%20that%20all%20the%20missing%20skiers%20are%20found%20alive%20%26amp%3B%20the%20reports%20of%20a%20casualty%20end%20up%20being%20unfounded.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECricketing%20legend%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%2C%20who%20is%20on%20a%20visit%20to%20Kashmir%2C%20was%20also%20on%20the%20way%20to%20Gulmarg%20which%20has%20recorded%20a%20bumper%20snowfall%20this%20week%20after%20a%20prolonged%20spell%20of%20dry%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20snow%20has%20brought%20cheer%20for%20the%20hotel%20industry%20and%20other%20local%20stakeholders.%20After%20the%20bumper%20snowfall%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20there%20have%20been%20frequent%20traffic%20jams%20on%20Gulmarg-Tangmarg%20road%20due%20to%20the%20heavy%20influx%20of%20domestic%20and%20foreign%20tourists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNearly%20all%20the%20hotels%20in%20Gulmarg%20are%20full%20and%20we%20are%20expecting%20the%20trend%20to%20continue%20for%20another%20two-three%20weeks%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20tourism%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20heavy%20snowfall%20in%20the%20higher%20reaches%20of%20Kashmir%20this%20week%2C%20officials%20have%20been%20issuing%20avalanche%20warnings%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%20A%20massive%20avalanche%20struck%20Sonamarg%20health%20resort%20in%20central%20Kashmir%20earlier%20this%20month%20but%20there%20were%20no%20fatalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20skiers%20have%20faced%20the%20wrath%20of%20deadly%20avalanches%20in%20Gulmarg.%20In%20February%20last%20year%2C%20two%20Polish%20skiers%20were%20killed%20and%20over%20a%20dozen%20were%20rescued%20when%20an%20avalanche%20struck%20the%20%E2%80%98backcountry%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20higher%20reaches%20of%20Gulmarg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20memory%2C%20the%20worst%20snow%20tragedy%20in%20Gulmarg%20took%20place%20in%202010%20when%20at%20least%2017%20Army%20soldiers%20were%20buried%20under%20an%20avalanche%20that%20hit%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20High%20Altitude%20Warfare%20School.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708613725000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17121316%2Fimad-clicks-Dg6tMlfSOQ4-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Frussian-skier-killed-six-others-rescued-after-avalanche-in-kashmirs-gulmarg%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20officials%2C%20seven%20skiers%20from%20Russia%20had%20planned%20a%20routine%20adventure%20run%20in%20Khilanmarg%20area%20of%20Gulmarg%20when%20an%20avalanche%20struck%20the%20area%20on%20Thursday%20afternoon%2C%20burying%20all%20of%20them%20along%20with%20a%20local%20guide.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Frussian-skier-killed-six-others-rescued-after-avalanche-in-kashmirs-gulmarg%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Palestinian%20gunmen%20kill%20Israeli%20man%20in%20West%20Bank%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708613135000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F37D2%2Fproduction%2F_132709241_36d58cc7875aea2db0e491a4dbbee83e564504c6.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68367493%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thirteen%20other%20people%20were%20hurt%20when%20three%20attackers%20shot%20at%20vehicles%20in%20a%20traffic%20jam%2C%20police%20say.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A55%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fn