nd%20attempt%2C%20as%20she%20fell%20short%20of%20going%20to%20the%20interview%20stage%20by%20a%20few%20marks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonal%20recounted%20this%20story%20alongside%20a%20picture%20of%20her%20UPSC%20Civil%20Services%202007%20Mains%20mark%20sheet%2C%20shared%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%20She%20reflected%20on%20the%20trials%20and%20tribulations%20that%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20her%20selection%20in%20May%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20remarkably%2C%20she%20achieved%20this%20feat%20while%20simultaneously%20pursuing%20her%20LLB%20(Bachelor%20of%20Laws)%20and%20working%20part-time%20as%20a%20Company%20Secretary%20(CS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20had%20low%20marks%20in%20the%20general%20studies%20paper%2C%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20qualify%20for%20the%20interview%20stage.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20this%20setback%20fueled%20my%20determination%20to%20leave%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20achieving%20my%20goal%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330545%2Fakshay-ridlan-qr-code-locket-finding-lost-missing-people-dementia-autism-upsc%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUPSC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20devoted%20herself%20to%20mastering%20the%20general%20studies%20paper%2C%20investing%20significant%20time%20and%20effort.%20Sonal%20also%20disclosed%20her%20strategy%20for%20excelling%20in%20the%20exams%20%E2%80%94%20which%20included%20meticulous%20note-taking%2C%20repeated%20revisions%2C%20and%20consistent%20practice%20in%20answer%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20diligent%20efforts%20bore%20fruit%20as%20she%20not%20only%20secured%20a%20commendable%20rank%20but%20also%20earned%20high%20marks%20in%20the%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20every%20aspirant%2C%20she%20shared%20this%20message%3A%20%E2%80%9CNo%20obstacle%20is%20insurmountable.%20Every%20setback%20and%20failure%20is%20an%20opportunity%20to%20learn%2C%20improvise%20and%20ultimately%2C%20trium