0was%20reportedly%20gone%20for%20'a%20while'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Lopez%20returned%20to%20his%20assigned%20seat%2C%20he%20%26quot%3Bbegan%20punching%20and%20hitting%26quot%3B%20the%20man%20seated%20across%20the%20aisle.%20Further%2C%20he%20tried%20to%20stab%20him%20in%20the%20eye.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20FBI%20agent%20wrote%20in%20court%20documents%2C%20%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20altercation%2C%20(the%20victim's)%20wife%20was%20screaming%20at%20the%20defendant%20to%20stop%20hitting%20her%20husband.%20(A%20witness)%20unbuckled%20her%20seatbelt%20and%20yelled%20at%20the%20defendant%20to%20stop.%26quot%3B%20The%20woman%2C%20who%20was%20protecting%20their%20seven-year-old%20son%2C%20was%20also%20struck%20by%20Lopez.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20witnesses%2C%20there%20%26quot%3Bwas%20blood%20everywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bpen%20and%20tape%20bundle%26quot%3B%20had%20dropped%20to%20the%20floor.%20The%20co-passenger%20is%20alive%20but%20he%20was%20severely%20injured.%20Lopez%20had%20walked%20to%20the%20front%20of%20the%20aircraft%20after%20the%20fight%2C%20yelling%2C%20%26quot%3BI'll%20only%20talk%20to%20the%20FBI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELopez%20was%20told%20to%20sit%20down%20by%20an%20onboard%20law%20enforcement%20official%2C%20and%20the%20flight%20attendants%20%26quot%3Bworked%20to%20provide%20flex%20cuffs%20and%20the%20defendant%20was%20restrained%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20flight.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20arrested%20by%20Las%20Vegas%20Metropolitan%20after%20the%20plane%20landed%20around%208%3A30%20am.%20The%20man%20said%20that%20he%20planned%20the%20assault%20because%20he%20%26quot%3Bfelt%20the%20mafia%20had%20been%20chasing%20him%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20had%20never%20seen%20the%20victim%20%26quot%3Bbut%20planned%20on%20killing%20him.%26quot%3B%20Additionally%2C%20he%20claimed%20that%20he%20armed%20himself%20with%20pens%20wrapped%20in%20rubber%20bands%20before%20boarding%20th