20VVPATs%3A%20Why%20Suspicions%20Persist%2C%20and%20Won't%20Subside%20Yet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F04112925%2FVoting_machine_in_India.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98s%20%E2%80%98India%20Black%20Boxed%E2%80%99%20series.%20Read%20it%20here%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fintroducing-india-black-boxed%5C%22%3EIntroduction%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fwhat-do-we-really-know-about-indias-gdp%5C%22%3EPart%20I%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fwhat-we-know-about-indias-post-covid-economy-recovery-and-rising-inequality%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPart%20II%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcomptroller-auditor-general-review-2014-2023-india-black-boxed%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPart%20III%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-the-union-govt-is-slowly-but-surely-blurring-indias-federal-structure%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPart%20IV%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-sabka-saath-sabka-vikas-hoax%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPart%20V%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhy-election-commissions-faqs-on-evm-vvpats-dont-clear-cloud-of-suspicion-over-electoral-process%5C%22%3Efirst%20part%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20aimed%20to%20delve%20deeper%20into%20certain%20responses%20provided%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20in%20its%20revised%20set%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eci.gov.in%2Fevm-faq-new%5C%22%3E100%20FAQs%3C%2Fa%3E%20(frequently%20asked%20questions)%20to%20demonstrate%20how%20unsatisfactory%20they%20are.%20The%20ECI%20released%20these%20updated%20FAQs%20on%20its%20website%20in%20January%20of%20this%20year%2C%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20addressing%20all%20doubts%20regarding%20these%20electoral%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20compared%20with%20the%20information%20contained%20in%20publicly%20available%20official%20documents%2C%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20claims%20about%20the%20design%2C%20and%20functioning%20of%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%20and%20Voter%20Verifiable%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20(VVPAT)%20units%2C%20raise%20more%20suspicion%20instead%20of%20resolving%20persistent%20doubts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20sequel%2C%20I%20address%20additional%20claims%20by%20ECI%2C%20considering%20the%20VVPAT%20patent-related%20documents%20and%20information%20revealed%20in%20response%20to%20formal%20requests%20under%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%2C%202005%20(RTI%20Act).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20piece%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20examined%20the%20following%20grey%20areas%20in%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20FAQs%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20is%20the%20correct%20expanded%20form%20of%20VVPAT%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDo%20we%20know%20enough%20about%20the%20microcontrollers%20used%20in%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20combo%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20correct%20expanded%20form%20of%20VVPAT%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20FAQ%20%231%2C%20the%20ECI%20addresses%20the%20question%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20an%20EVM%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CEVM%20stands%20for%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machine.%20It%20is%20a%20device%20used%20to%20electronically%20record%20and%20count%20votes%20cast%20in%20elections.%20The%20Indian%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machine%20(EVM)%20system%20is%20also%20termed%20as%20ECI-EVM%2C%20meaning%20an%20EVM%20specifically%20designed%2C%20manufactured%20and%20used%20for%20Elections%20as%20per%20election%20procedure%20and%20rules%20framed%20by%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20and%20documented%20in%20manual%20on%20EVM%2C%20so%20as%20to%20differentiate%20it%20from%20EVMs%20used%20in%20other%20countries.%20ECI%20%E2%80%93%20EVM%20consists%20of%20Ballot%20Unit%20(BU)%2C%20Control%20Unit%20(CU)%20and%20the%20later%20added%20Voter%20Verifiable%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20(VVPAT)%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20ECI%2C%20VVPAT%20stands%20for%20%E2%80%9CVoter%20Verifiable%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%E2%80%9D.%20The%20reader%20is%20expected%20to%20believe%20that%20this%20is%20the%20correct%20expansion%20of%20that%20abbreviation.%20However%20other%20official%20documents%20tell%20a%20different%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20specific%20mention%20of%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98VVPAT%E2%80%99%20or%20its%20expansion%20in%20the%20primary%20election%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20law%20which%20governs%20the%20conduct%20of%20elections%20and%20voting%20in%20India%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flddashboard.legislative.gov.in%2Felectionlawsrelated%2Frepresentation-people-act-1951-act-no-43-1951%5C%22%3Ethe%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%2C%201951%3C%2Fa%3E%20(RPA).%20The%20lone%20provision%20which%20enables%20the%20use%20of%20electronic%20voting%20in%20elections%20to%20parliament%20and%20the%20State%20Legislatures%20is%20Section%2061A%20is%20reproduced%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C61A%20%E2%80%93%20voting%20machines%20at%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20Notwithstanding%20anything%20contained%20in%20this%20Act%20or%20the%20rules%20made%20thereunder%2C%20the%20giving%20and%20recording%20of%20votes%20by%20voting%20machines%20in%20such%20manner%20as%20may%20be%20prescribed%2C%20may%20be%20adopted%20in%20such%20constituency%20or%20constituencies%20as%20the%20Election%20Commission%20may%2C%20having%20regard%20to%20the%20circumstances%20of%20each%20case%2C%20specify.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98voting%20machine%E2%80%99%20means%20any%20machine%20or%20apparatus%20whether%20operated%20electronically%20or%20otherwise%20used%20for%20giving%20or%20recording%20of%20votes%20and%20any%20reference%20to%20a%20ballot%20box%20or%20ballot%20paper%20in%20this%20Act%20or%20the%20rules%20made%20thereunder%20shall%2C%20save%20as%20otherwise%20provided%2C%20be%20construed%20as%20including%20a%20reference%20to%20such%20voting%20machine%20wherever%20such%20voting%20machine%20is%20used%20at%20any%20election.%E2%80%9D%20(This%20provision%20was%20inserted%20through%20an%20amendment%20in%201989.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20reference%20to%20VVPATs%20in%20the%20above%20provision%2C%20nor%20can%20it%20be%20found%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flegislative.gov.in%2Fmanual-of-election-law-volume-ii%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20Conduct%20of%20Election%20Rules%2C%201961%3C%2Fa%3E%20(CoER)%2C%20which%20contains%20the%20details%20of%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20RPA%20will%20be%20implemented.%20In%202013%2C%20a%20proviso%20each%20to%20Rule%2049A%20and%2049M%20and%20two%20new%20rules%20%E2%80%93%2049MA%20and%2056D%20%E2%80%93%20were%20introduced%20through%20an%20amendment%20to%20the%20CoER%2C%20to%20facilitate%20the%20use%20of%20VVPATs%20in%20conjunction%20with%20EVMs.%20(Other%20relevant%20rules%20were%20also%20tweaked%20to%20incorporate%20reference%20to%20this%20change%20in%20the%20electronic%20voting%20and%20counting%20system).%20The%20contents%20of%20these%20statutory%20insertions%20are%20also%20hyperlinked%20to%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20FAQs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20what%20is%20noteworthy%20in%20these%20amendments%20is%20the%20complete%20absence%20of%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9CVVPAT%E2%80%9D%20or%20an%20expansion%20of%20this%20abbreviation.%20Instead%2C%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%9Cprinter%20for%20paper%20trail%E2%80%9D%20or%20its%20derivations%20are%20used%20in%20the%20amendments.%20So%2C%20to%20the%20best%20of%20our%20knowledge%2C%20the%20nomenclature%20%E2%80%9CVoter%20Verifiable%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%E2%80%9D%20has%20no%20statutory%20mention%2C%20either%20in%20the%201989%20amendment%20to%20the%20RPA%20or%20in%20the%202013%20amendments%20to%20the%20CoER.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20did%20the%20ECI%20coin%20this%20phrase%20and%20the%20related%20abbreviation%20is%20a%20question%20which%20is%20not%20explained%20in%20its%20FAQs%20or%20the%20related%20Annexures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-anatomy-of-an-electronic-voting-machine-what-we-know-and-what-we-dont%5C%22%3E%20The%20Anatomy%20of%20an%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machine%3A%20What%20We%20Know%20and%20What%20We%20Don%E2%80%99t%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVVPAT%20is%20expanded%20differently%20in%20the%20patent-related%20records%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20answer%20to%20FAQ%20%237%2C%20Bharat%20Electronics%20Limited%20(BEL)%2C%20which%20comes%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%2C%20and%20Electronics%20Corporation%20of%20India%20Limited%20(ECIL)%2C%20which%20comes%20under%20the%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%2C%20have%20a%20duopoly%20on%20the%20supply%20of%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%20for%20parliamentary%20and%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20discussed%20in%20the%20first%20part%2C%20only%20BEL%20has%20been%20officially%20granted%20a%20patent%20for%20the%20production%20of%20VVPATs%20in%20May%202022.%20(This%20was%20done%20after%20the%20completion%20of%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EECIL%E2%80%99s%20patent%20application%20for%20a%20VVPAT%20machine%20is%20not%20available%20on%20this%20database%2C%20so%20it%20may%20be%20presumed%20that%20there%20is%20some%20working%20arrangement%20between%20the%20two%20CPSUs%20for%20manufacturing%20the%20VVPAT%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20copy%20of%20the%20order%20granting%20the%20patent%20to%20BEL%20by%20the%20Controller%20General%20of%20Patents%2C%20Designs%2C%20Trademarks%2C%20and%20Geographical%20Indications%20mentions%20the%20expansion%20of%20VVPAT%20as%20%E2%80%9CVoter%20%3Cem%3EVerified%3C%2Fem%3E%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%E2%80%9D%20and%20not%20%E2%80%9CVoter%20%3Cem%3EVerifiable%3C%2Fem%3E%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImages%20of%20the%20patent%20order%20and%20its%20communication%20to%20BEL%20by%20the%20Chennai%20Patents%20Office%20testify%20to%20this%20fact%20%3Cem%3E(see%20images%201%20and%202%20below)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21131632%2FImage-1-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22849%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21131632%2FImage-1-1.jpg%20849w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21131632%2FImage-1-1-212x300.jpg%20212w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21131632%2FImage-1-1-724x1024.jpg%20724w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698148%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImage%201.%20A%20copy%20of%20the%20government%20order%20granting%20the%20VVPAT%20patent%20and%20its%20communication%20to%20BEL%20through%20their%20Patent%20Agent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21131747%2FImage-2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22835%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21131747%2FImage-2.jpg%20835w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21131747%2FImage-2-228x300.jpg%20228w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21131747%2FImage-2-777x1024.jpg%20777w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698150%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221100%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImage%202.%20A%20copy%20of%20the%20government%20order%20granting%20the%20VVPAT%20patent%20and%20its%20communication%20to%20BEL%20through%20their%20Patent%20Agent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20phrase%20%E2%80%9CVoter%20%3Cem%3EVerified%3C%2Fem%3E%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%E2%80%9D%20is%20also%20recorded%20on%20the%20patent%20certificate%20granted%20to%20BEL%20as%20part%20of%20the%20decision-making%20procedure%20%3Cem%3E(see%20image%203%20below)%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%20case%20readers%20begin%20to%20speculate%2C%20the%20Patents%20Office%20may%20have%20made%20an%20error%20in%20the%20name%20due%20to%20bureaucratic%20procedures%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20worth%20noting%20that%20this%20is%20precisely%20how%20BEL%20named%20the%20VVPAT%20in%20the%20complete%20specifications%20submitted%20along%20with%20the%20patent%20application%20%3Cem%3E(see%20image%204%20below)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21133241%2Fimage-1850.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21133241%2Fimage-1850.png%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21133241%2Fimage-1850-300x210.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698159%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22448%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImages%203%20and%204%3A%20A%20copy%20of%20the%20patent%20certificate%20issued%20and%20the%20front%20page%20of%20the%20VVPAT%E2%80%99s%3Cbr%3Ecomplete%20specifications%20submitted%20by%20BEL.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20this%20significant%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReaders%20might%20call%20this%20nitpicking.%20%E2%80%9CVerifiable%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Cverified%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20what%20difference%20does%20it%20make%20as%20long%20as%20the%20VVPAT%20machine%20does%20what%20it%20is%20required%20to%20do%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20question%20I%20raised%20before%20the%20concluding%20segment%20of%20the%20first%20part%2C%20which%20concerned%20the%20vote%20that%20must%20be%20counted%2C%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20this%20semantic%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20%E2%80%9Cverifiable%E2%80%9D%20only%20refers%20to%20the%20potential%20of%20the%20machine%20%E2%80%93%20to%20show%20a%20slip%20recording%20the%20name%2C%20symbol%2C%20and%20serial%20number%20in%20whose%20favour%20the%20voter%20clicked%20on%20the%20Ballot%20Unit%20(BU)%20so%20that%20he%20or%20she%20may%20be%20satisfied%20with%20it%20and%20nothing%20more.%20The%20term%20%E2%80%9Cverified%E2%80%9D%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20indicates%20a%20certainty%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20slip%20has%20been%20verified%20by%20the%20voter%20before%20it%20cuts%20and%20falls%20down%20into%20the%20Drop%20Box%20in%20the%20VVPAT%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20is%20it%20not%20the%20VVPAT%20slip%20that%20must%20be%20counted%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cvote%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20the%20voter%20verifies%20as%20a%20correct%20record%20of%20his%20or%20her%20choice%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20electronic%20tally%20recorded%20in%20the%20control%20unit%20(CU)%3F%20This%20is%20why%20use%20of%20the%20correct%20nomenclature%20becomes%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EECI%E2%80%99s%20longwinded%20answers%20to%20FAQs%20%2362%20and%2063%20based%20on%20its%20defensive%20claims%20of%20scientific%20sampling%20of%20five%20VVPAT%20Units%2C%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20tallying%20those%20slips%20with%20the%20candidate%20totals%20from%20the%20CU%2C%20are%20simply%20unconvincing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20we%20know%20enough%20about%20the%20microcontrollers%20used%20in%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20combo%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMicrocontrollers%20form%20the%20nerve%20centre%20of%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20combo.%20Extracts%20from%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20FAQs%2C%20which%20explain%20what%20the%20microcontrollers%20do%2C%20are%20reproduced%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFAQ%20%2342%20%3C%2Fem%3Esays%2C%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20ECI%20says%20an%20EVM%20can%20be%20programmed%20only%20once%2C%20making%20hacking%20unlikely.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20reports%20that%20it%20can%20be%20programmed%20several%20times.%20There%20are%20other%20reports%20saying%20that%20EVM%20machines%20can%20be%20manipulated%20by%20connecting%20it%20to%20cell%20phones%2C%20Bluetooth%20devices%2C%20replacing%20parts%20of%20it%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20manipulation%2C%20apart%20from%20physical%20replacement%20of%20it%20by%20other%20EVMs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20query%20is%20explained%20as%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ECI-EVM%20use%20secure%20controllers%20which%20can%20disable%20further%20programming%20after%20a%20step%20known%20as%20one-time-programming%20(OTP).%20%3Cem%3EThe%20technical%20information%20about%20the%20micro%20controllers%20is%20available%20in%20public%20domain%20and%20can%20be%20accessed%20on%20the%20website%20of%20micro%20controller%20manufacturers%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFAQ%20%2346%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20claimed%20that%20EVM%20machines%20can%20be%20manipulated%20by%20connecting%20it%20to%20cell%20phones%2C%20Bluetooth%20devices%2C%20replacing%20parts%20of%20it%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20manipulation%2C%20apart%20from%20physical%20replacement%20of%20it%20by%20other%20EVMs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20query%20is%20explained%20as%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20claim%20is%20baseless%20and%20unscientific%20claim.%20The%20technical%20information%20about%20the%20microcontrollers%20is%20available%20in%20public%20domain%20and%20can%20be%20accessed%20on%20the%20website%20of%20microcontroller%20manufacturers.%20The%20EVMs%20%2F%20VVPATs%20use%20controllers%20which%20are%20One%20Time%20Programmable%20(OTP).%20This%20feature%20is%20activated%20by%20a%20code%20%2Fcommand%2C%20fed%20via%20a%20software%20program%2C%20and%20in%20the%20first%20time%20run%20at%20power%20%E2%80%98on%E2%80%99%20sets%20an%20internal%20register%20to%20shut%20off%20any%20re-programmability%20capability.%20%3Cu%3EThe%20code%20%2F%20command%20and%20procedure%20are%20also%20available%20in%20public%20domain%20in%20the%20datasheets%2F%20application%20notes%20on%20use%20of%20these%20microcontrollers%3C%2Fu%3E%E2%80%A6.%E2%80%9D%20(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFAQ%20%2348%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CCan%20the%20details%20of%20the%20EVM%20microcontrollers%20be%20explained%20along%20with%20the%20OTP%20features%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20explained%20as%2C%20%E2%80%9CBoth%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20use%20standard%20microcontrollers%20available%20off%20the%20shelf%20and%20hence%20all%20information%20on%20the%20microcontrollers%20is%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20via%20manufacturers%E2%80%99%20data%20sheets%2F%20application%20notes%20and%20user%20manuals.%20The%20One%20Time%20Programmable%20(OTP)%20feature%20is%20not%20activated%20by%20any%20hardware%20or%20pin-based%20signal%2Fcommand%20at%20external%20pins%20of%20the%20microcontrollers%2C%20rather%20this%20code%2F%20command%20is%20fed%20via%20a%20software%20programme%20and%20in%20the%20first%20time%20%E2%80%9Crun%E2%80%9D%20at%20power%20on%20sets%20an%20internal%20register%20to%20shut%20off%20any%20re-programmability.%20Once%20this%20is%20done%20the%20programme%20cannot%20be%20changed.%20%3Cu%3EThe%20procedure%20is%20available%20in%20public%20domain%20in%20the%20datasheets%20%2F%20user%20manuals%20on%20use%20of%20the%20microcontrollers%3C%2Fu%3E.%E2%80%9D%20(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ECI%20asserts%2C%20not%20once%20but%20thrice%2C%20that%20information%20about%20microcontrollers%20used%20in%20the%20EVM%20is%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20It%20also%20says%20that%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20purchase%20them%20off%20the%20shelf.%20That%20may%20be%20so%20and%20I%20do%20not%20have%20any%20reason%20to%20dispute%20that%20claim.%20But%20do%20we%20know%20from%20which%20manufacturer%E2%80%99s%20shelf%20these%20companies%20buy%20the%20microcontrollers%3F%20Neither%20the%20ECI%20nor%20the%20two%20companies%20have%20publicly%20disclosed%20the%20names%20of%20the%20microcontroller%20manufacturers%2Fsuppliers%20on%20their%20own.%20The%20only%20time%20we%20officially%20got%20to%20know%20of%20the%20identity%20of%20one%20such%20manufacturer%2Fsupplier%20was%20from%20BEL%E2%80%99s%20reply%20to%20one%20of%20my%20RTI%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbel-refuses-to-disclose-evm-vvpat-data-even-after-demanding-fees-what-does-it-mean%5C%22%3EBEL%20Refuses%20to%20Disclose%20EVM%2C%20VVPAT%20Data%20Even%20After%20Demanding%20Fees.%20What%20Does%20It%20Mean%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202019%2C%20identical%20RTI%20applications%20were%20filed%20with%20BEL%2C%20seeking%20the%20complete%20list%20of%20manufacturers%20of%20microcontrollers%20used%20in%20the%20latest%20generation%20(M3)%20EVMs%2C%20along%20with%20their%20postal%20addresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20BEL%E2%80%99s%20Central%20Public%20Information%20Officer%20(CPIO)%20replied%20with%20the%20model%20number%20of%20the%20microcontroller%20used%20in%20the%20EVMs%20%3Cem%3E(see%20image%205%20below)%3C%2Fem%3E.%20ECIL%E2%80%99s%20CPIO%20denied%20access%20to%20the%20same%20information%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20%E2%80%98classified%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20invoked%20the%20national%20security%20exemption%20under%20Section%208(1)(a)%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act.%20%3Cem%3E(See%20image%206%20below)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21134823%2Fimage-1851.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22623%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21134823%2Fimage-1851.png%20623w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21134823%2Fimage-1851-300x208.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698170%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22432%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImages%205%20%26amp%3B%206%3A%20RTI%20replies%20of%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20regarding%20the%20manufacturers%20of%20microcontrollers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EECIL%E2%80%99s%20denial%20and%20BEL%E2%80%99s%20rejection%20of%20other%20RTI%20queries%20were%20challenged%20all%20the%20way%20up%20to%20the%20Central%20Information%20Commission%20(CIC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202021%2C%20the%20CIC%20strangely%20remanded%20the%20matter%20back%20to%20the%20respective%20first%20appellate%20authorities%20(FAAs)%20to%20decide%20the%20matter%20afresh%2C%20without%20examining%20the%20correctness%20of%20their%20decisions%20on%20its%20own%2C%20as%20it%20ought%20to%20have%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EECIL%E2%80%99s%20FAA%20directed%20its%20CPIO%20to%20provide%20a%20%E2%80%9Cproper%20explanation%2Fjustification%E2%80%9D%20for%20claiming%20exemption%20against%20revealing%20the%20microcontroller-related%20information%20(amongst%20others)%20because%20I%20had%20shown%20that%20BEL%20had%20already%20provided%20this%20information%20%3Cem%3E(see%20image%207%20below)%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20CPIO%20invoked%20third-party%20interests%20and%20denied%20the%20names%20of%20the%20microcontroller%20manufacturers%2Fsuppliers%20by%20invoking%20Section%208(1)(d)%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act%20%3Cem%3E(see%20image%208%20below).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21144506%2Fimage-1853.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22616%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21144506%2Fimage-1853.png%20616w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21144506%2Fimage-1853-300x209.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698179%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22430%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImages%207%20%26amp%3B%208%3A%20ECIL%20FAA%E2%80%99s%20order%20post%20CIC%20decision%20and%20CPIO%E2%80%99s%20subsequent%20reply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20these%20prolonged%20RTI%20interventions%2C%20the%20ECI%20cannot%20claim%20with%20a%20straight%20face%20that%20information%20about%20the%20microcontrollers%20is%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20Even%20if%20it%20were%2C%20voters%20can%20only%20access%20it%20if%20the%20names%20of%20the%20manufacturers%2Fsuppliers%20are%20made%20public.%20Otherwise%2C%20this%20information%20remains%20trapped%20in%20a%20black%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Felection-commissions-faqs-on-evms-dont-really-address-major-design-deficiencies%5C%22%3EElection%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20FAQs%20on%20EVMs%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Really%20Address%20Major%20Design%20Deficiencies%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20microcontrollers%2C%20used%20by%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%2C%20only%20one-time-programmable%20(OTP)%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20this%20was%20my%20initial%20foray%20into%20the%20world%20of%20EVMs%2C%20the%20query%20was%20negligently%20drafted%2C%20leaving%20out%20a%20reference%20to%20VVPAT%20in%20the%20RTI%20query%20relating%20to%20microcontrollers.%20I%20ended%20up%20asking%20only%20about%20EVM%20microcontrollers%2C%20as%20I%20had%20not%20read%20the%20relevant%20patent%20documents%20about%20VVPATs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20discussed%20in%20the%20first%20part%2C%20we%20know%20for%20a%20fact%20that%20both%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20were%20granted%20patents%20for%20the%20EVMs%20in%202006.%20Both%20companies%20disclosed%20the%20presence%20of%20microcontrollers%20in%20the%20CUs%20of%20their%20EVMs%20to%20the%20Patents%20Controller%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20need%20under%20the%20patents%20law%20to%20mention%20the%20names%20of%20manufacturers%20of%20any%20component%20of%20the%20machine%20sought%20to%20be%20patented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20while%20BEL%20claimed%20that%20the%20microcontroller%20it%20was%20using%20was%20one-time-programmable%20(OTP)%2C%20ECIL%20staked%20no%20such%20claim%20%3Cem%3E(see%20images%209%20and%2010%20below).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22153702%2Fimage-1854.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22623%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22153702%2Fimage-1854.png%20623w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22153702%2Fimage-1854-300x215.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698357%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22447%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EExtract%20from%20the%20complete%20specifications%20about%20EVMs%20submitted%20by%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20respectively%2C%20to%20the%20Patents%20Controller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20a%20complete%20believer%20in%20their%20infallibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImage%209%20is%20an%20extract%20from%20the%20complete%20specifications%20of%20the%20EVM%2C%20which%20BEL%20submitted%20to%20the%20Patents%20Controller%2C%20where%20the%20microcontroller%20is%20described%20as%20OTP%20type.%20Image%2010%20is%20an%20extract%20from%20the%20complete%20specifications%20of%20the%20EVM%2C%20which%20ECIL%20submitted%20to%20the%20Patents%20Controller%2C%20where%20the%20microcontroller%20is%20not%20described%20as%20OTP%20type.%20Further%2C%20ECIL%E2%80%99s%20description%20of%20what%20the%20CU%20can%20do%20with%20its%20microcontroller%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Ccollect%2C%20record%2C%20store%2C%20count%20and%20display%20the%20votes%20when%20called%20for%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20completely%20obviates%20any%20possibility%20that%20it%20is%20one-time-programmable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20EVM%20machines%20are%20intended%20for%20repeated%20use%20across%20multiple%20elections%2C%20it%20is%20logical%20to%20assume%20that%20the%20microcontroller%20utilised%20by%20ECIL%20must%20be%20rewriteable.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20assertion%20that%20the%20microcontrollers%20employed%20by%20both%20companies%20are%20of%20the%20OTP%20type%20does%20not%20appear%20very%20convincing.%20Unless%20ECIL%20has%20since%20altered%20the%20design%20of%20its%20CU%20to%20mirror%20the%20OTP-type%20microcontroller%20used%20by%20BEL%2C%20there%20is%20hardly%20any%20information%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20regarding%20such%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20many%20microcontrollers%20are%20used%20in%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20combo%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20confirmed%20from%20the%20patent-related%20documents%20discussed%20above%20that%20there%20is%20indeed%20a%20microcontroller%20within%20the%20CU%20of%20the%20EVMs%20manufactured%20by%20both%20companies.%20BEL%E2%80%99s%20patent%20application%20documents%20further%20disclose%20that%20its%20VVPAT%20machine%20also%20contains%20at%20least%20one%20microcontroller%20and%20suggest%20the%20potential%20existence%20of%20multiple%20such%20microcontrollers%20%3Cem%3E(see%20images%2011%20and%2012%20below)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22154919%2Fimage-1855.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22631%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22154919%2Fimage-1855.png%20631w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22154919%2Fimage-1855-300x200.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698358%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22420%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImages%2011%20and%2012%3A%20Extracts%20from%20BEL%E2%80%99s%20complete%20specifications%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20machine%20submitted%20to%20the%20Patents%20Controller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20paragraph%20no.%200053%20of%20the%20complete%20specifications%20submitted%20to%20the%20Patents%20Controller%20while%20applying%20for%20a%20patent%2C%20BEL%20states%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%5B0053%5D%20In%20an%20aspect%2C%20the%20sensitive%20hardware%20may%20be%20one%20or%20more%20artefacts%20such%20as%20but%20not%20limited%20to%20%3Cem%3Eone-time%20programmable%20microcontroller%2C%20associated%20storage%20comprising%20of%20computational%20program%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20sensitive%20data%20and%20configuration%20information%20among%20other%20things.%E2%80%9D%20(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20at%20paragraph%20no.%2000136%20of%20the%20same%20document%2C%20BEL%20states%20as%20follows%2C%20in%20the%20context%20of%20a%20detailed%20description%20of%20the%20drawings%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20machine%20submitted%20to%20the%20Patents%20Controller%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%5B00136%5D%20In%20another%20aspect%2C%20%3Cem%3Evarious%20software%20for%20control%20and%20operation%20of%20the%20proposed%20system%20can%20be%20held%20in%20appropriately%20configured%20one%20or%20more%20controllers%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20absolutely%20secure%20formats%20so%20that%20such%20software%20may%20not%20be%20tampered%20with%2C%20without%20errors%20being%20triggered.%20%3Cu%3EMicrocontrollers%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3Cem%3Eused%20in%20the%20proposed%20system%20can%20be%20of%20one%20time%20programmable%20type%20and%20used%20to%20store%20firmware%20that%20cannot%20be%20changed%20or%20modified%20once%20fused.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20combined%20reading%20of%20the%20two%20claims%20made%20by%20BEL%20indicates%20the%20use%20of%20at%20least%20one%20more%20OTP-type%20microcontroller%20in%20its%20VVPAT%20machine%2C%20which%20is%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20microcontroller%20used%20in%20the%20CU%20of%20the%20EVM.%20That%20is%20not%20all%2C%20in%20the%20same%20document%2C%20BEL%20claims%20that%20there%20is%20another%20associated%20storage%20component%20which%20will%20contain%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccomputational%20program%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20this%20will%20be%20the%20%E2%80%98artefact%20into%20which%20the%20candidate%20names%2C%20symbols%20and%20serial%20numbers%20are%20loaded%20during%20every%20election.%20So%2C%20this%20artefact%20(not%20being%20a%20hardware%20or%20software%20engineer%2C%20I%20hesitate%20to%20call%20them%20a%20%E2%80%98microcontroller%E2%80%99)%20cannot%20possibly%20be%20OTP-type.%20Who%20is%20supplying%20this%20artefact%2Fdevice%20is%20a%20mystery%20hidden%20inside%20a%20black%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fevm-voting-machine-election-polls%5C%22%3EThe%20Term%20%E2%80%98EVM%E2%80%99%20No%20Longer%20Serves%20Us.%20We%20Need%20to%20Understand%20%E2%80%98Electronic%20Voting%20Systems%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20kind%20of%20memory%20does%20NXP%20microcontroller%20have%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20BEL%E2%80%99s%20CPIO%20wittingly%20or%20unwittingly%20disclosed%20the%20model%20number%20of%20the%20microcontroller%20in%20response%20to%20the%202019%20RTI%20application.%20The%20webpage%20of%20the%20company%20NXP%2C%20from%20which%20BEL%20purchased%20the%20microcontroller%2C%20explains%20that%20the%20model%20type%2C%20NXP-MK61FX512VMD12%2C%20features%20not%20just%20one%2C%20but%20three%20types%20of%20memory.%20Among%20these%2C%20one%20is%20OTP%20type%2C%20and%20another%20is%20rewriteable%2C%20akin%20to%20the%20memory%20found%20in%20commonly%20used%20pen%2Fflash%20drives%20%3Cem%3E(see%20images%2013%20and%2014%20below)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22160027%2Fimage-1856.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22836%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22160027%2Fimage-1856.png%20675w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22160027%2Fimage-1856-300x204.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698361%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22567%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImages%2013%20and%2014%3A%20Product%20description%20of%20the%20NXP-MK61FX512VMD12%20microcontroller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-anatomy-of-an-electronic-voting-machine-what-we-know-and-what-we-dont%5C%22%3Emade%20this%20information%20public%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202019%2C%20and%20the%20media%20covered%20it%20widely%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20always%20labelled%20the%20microcontroller%20as%20an%20OTP-type.%20It%20is%20quite%20a%20relief%20to%20see%20the%20Commission%20acknowledging%20this%20fact%20in%20its%20FAQ%20%2353%20reproduced%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cstrong%3EFAQ53.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20the%20VVPAT%20have%20a%20programmable%20memory%3F%20If%20yes%2C%20then%20at%20what%20stages%20in%20the%20election%20process%20is%20it%20accessed%20by%20an%20external%20device%3F%20If%20no%2C%20then%20where%20are%20the%20names%20and%20symbols%20of%20the%20candidates%20stored%20in%20the%20VVPAT%20for%20it%20to%20print%20the%20same%20in%20theVVPAT%20slip%20later%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnswer%3A%20%3Cem%3EA%20VVPAT%20has%20two%20different%20memories.%20One%2C%20where%20the%20program%20instructions%20are%20kept%20for%20the%20microcontrollers%2C%20is%20One%20Time%20Programmed%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E(OTP).%20The%20VVPAT%20firmware%20is%20stored%20in%20the%20One%20Time%20Programmed%20memory%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E.%20%3C%2Fem%3EAfter%20the%20firmware%20is%20ported%20in%20the%20microcontroller%20at%20the%20manufacturers%E2%80%99%20site%2C%20no%20changes%20in%20the%20program%20are%20possible%20subsequently.%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20other%20memory%20is%20for%20storing%20graphical%20images%20containing%20serial%20number%2C%20name%2C%20and%20symbol%20of%20the%20candidates%20as%20data%3C%2Fu%3E.%20%3C%2Fem%3EThis%20is%20done%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20symbol%20loading%20unit%2C%20during%20the%20commissioning%20of%20VVPATs%20before%20each%20election.%20Live%20display%20of%20the%20symbols%20being%20loaded%20into%20the%20VVPAT%20is%20done%20during%20the%20Commissioning%20process%20in%20presence%20of%20candidates%2Ftheir%20representatives%20to%20make%20the%20process%20more%20transparent.%E2%80%9D%20(emphasis%20supplied)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20the%20ECI%20does%20not%20tell%20us%20is%20whether%20the%20same%20NXP-manufactured%20microcontroller%20is%20used%20in%20the%20CU%20of%20the%20EVM%20and%20also%20the%20VVPAT%20(for%20two%20types%20of%20uses%20%E2%80%93%20one%20for%20programme%20instructions%20and%20another%20for%20storing%20the%20candidate-related%20information%20and%20images%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20only%20one%20of%20the%20NXP%20chips%20one-time%20programmed%20while%20the%20others%20are%20rewriteable%3F%20Or%20do%20BEL%20and%20ECIL%20use%20other%20brands%20of%20rewriteable%20microcontrollers%3F%20Is%20the%20pattern%20of%20microcontroller%20usage%20similar%20in%20both%20BEL-%20and%20ECIL-manufactured%20machines%3F%20ECIL%20did%20not%20claim%20in%20its%20EVM%20patent%20documents%20that%20the%20microcontroller%20it%20uses%20are%20OTP%20type.%20Has%20that%20changed%20now%3F%20The%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20FAQs%20are%20silent%20about%20these%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConclusion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20matter%20of%20grave%20concern%20is%20the%20November%202023%20media%20revelation%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farstechnica.com%2Fsecurity%2F2023%2F11%2Fhackers-spent-2-years-looting-secrets-of-chipmaker-nxp-before-being-detected%2F%5C%22%3ENXP%20was%20the%20victim%20of%20an%20espionage%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%202017%20and%202020.%20Despite%20this%2C%20the%20company%20reportedly%20neglected%20to%20inform%20its%20customers%20individually%20about%20these%20developments.%20It%20is%20confirmed%20that%20at%20least%20BEL%2C%20if%20not%20ECIL%2C%20procured%20microcontrollers%20from%20NXP%20during%20this%20period.%20The%20extent%20to%20which%20this%20may%20have%20affected%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20units%20produced%20by%20BEL%2C%20which%20serves%20as%20the%20Election%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20supplier%20year%20after%20year%2C%20remains%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20poses%20a%20significant%20national%20security%20concern%20that%20both%20the%20Election%20Commission%20and%20the%20companies%20utilising%20NXP%20microcontrollers%20must%20address%20to%20all%20voters%20before%20the%20next%20round%20of%20elections.%20When%20crucial%20information%20is%20withheld%20within%20a%20black%20box%2C%20suspicions%20will%20only%20continue%20to%20linger.%20These%20elections%20belong%20to%20us%2C%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20units%20are%20machines%20funded%20and%20utilized%20by%20us%2C%20the%20people.%20Hence%2C%20WE%20THE%20PEOPLE%20have%20the%20right%20to%20demand%20more%20transparency%20than%20what%20the%20ECI%20has%20disclosed%20thus%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVenkatesh%20Nayak%20is%20director%2C%20Commonwealth%20Human%20Rights%20Initiative%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20All%20facts%20narrated%20above%20are%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20Views%20expressed%20are%20personal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708605051000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F04112925%2FVoting_machine_in_India.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fevms-and-vvpats-why-suspicions-persist-and-wont-subside-yet%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20discrepancy%20in%20the%20expansion%20of%20VVPAT%2C%20recorded%20as%20%26quot%3BVoter%20Verified%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%26quot%3B%20in%20patent-related%20records%2C%20raises%20questions%20about%20the%20legitimacy%20and%20functioning%20of%20these%20voting%20systems.%20Moreover%2C%20do%20we%20know%20enough%20about%20the%20microcontrollers%20used%20in%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20combo%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fevms-and-vvpats-why-suspicions-persist-and-wont-subside-yet%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%3A%20The%20Only%20Certainty%20After%20a%20Rigged%20Election%20Is%20Chaos%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22145025%2FUntitled-design-7.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20two%20weeks%20after%20one%20of%20the%20most%20tainted%20elections%20in%20the%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20checkered%20parliamentary%20history%2C%20a%20coalition%20government%20is%20in%20sight.%20But%20the%20only%20certainty%20that%20has%20emerged%20is%20instability%20and%20political%20chaos.%20And%20it%20may%20only%20get%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20aphorism%20goes%20that%20the%20Pakistan%20army%20has%20never%20won%20a%20war%20and%20never%20lost%20an%20election.%20The%20army%20might%20not%20have%20lost%20this%20one%20either%20but%20appears%20to%20have%20botched%20the%20manipulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brass%20had%20intended%20and%20plotted%20for%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Imran%20Khan%20to%20be%20routed%20at%20the%20polls%2C%20thus%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20purging%20him%20out%20of%20the%20political%20system.%20It%20envisaged%20a%20new%20dispensation%20along%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fe.jang.com.pk%2Fdetail%2F624671%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fe.jang.com.pk%2Fdetail%2F624671%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1xUtPI6MJWSVCgvH5thHBE%5C%22%3Eso-called%20Bangladesh%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20diarchal%20controlled%20democracy%20in%20which%20the%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20(PMLN)%20alone%2C%20or%20in%20a%20coalition%20with%20the%20Pakistan%20Peoples%20Party%20(PPP)%20and%20others%2C%20would%20form%20a%20stable%20government.%20But%20the%20election%20results%20stunned%20everyone%2C%20including%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20planners%20and%20conventional%20political%20prognosticators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndependent%20candidates%20backed%20by%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20Pakistan%20Tehrik-e-Insaf%20(PTI)%20party%2C%20swept%20the%20polls%20for%20the%20Khyber-Pakhtunkhwa%E2%80%99s%20(KP)%20provincial%20legislature%20and%20won%20a%20plurality%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20National%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%20elections%2C%20the%20military%20establishment%20had%20thrown%20everything%20but%20the%20kitchen%20sink%20at%20its%20former%20prot%C3%A9g%C3%A9%20Khan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-election-no-matter-who-wins-the-army-will-rule-the-roost%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-election-no-matter-who-wins-the-army-will-rule-the-roost%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1VwNRXajI4eXSGItW4wpDw%5C%22%3Eto%20keep%20him%20from%20returning%20to%20power%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20PTI%2C%20with%20its%20electoral%20machinery%20already%20depleted%20after%20the%20army%20induced%20defections%20and%20break-away%20factions%2C%20was%20kept%20from%20running%20as%20a%20party%20by%20denying%20it%20an%20election%20symbol.%20Khan%2C%20who%20has%20already%20been%20in%20jail%2C%20was%20slapped%20with%20egregious%20sentences%2C%20including%20a%20grotesque%20one%20for%20an%20unlawful%20marriage%20under%20Islamic%20conventions%2C%20just%20days%20before%20the%20polls.%20The%20party%E2%80%99s%20election%20campaign%20was%20run%20by%20its%20third%20and%20fourth-tier%20leadership%2C%20comprising%20mostly%20of%20lawyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20made%20effective%20use%20of%20the%20new%20media%20platforms%20like%20TikTok%20to%20run%20campaign%20ads%20and%20held%20virtual%20rallies%20on%20Twitter%20and%20Facebook.%20In%20a%20first%20for%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20party%20used%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2Fvideo%2F2023%2Fdec%2F18%2Fpakistans-imran-khan-uses-ai-crafted-speech-to-call-for-votes-from-prison-video%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2Fvideo%2F2023%2Fdec%2F18%2Fpakistans-imran-khan-uses-ai-crafted-speech-to-call-for-votes-from-prison-video%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw22KQ88aZeQF6KJroOYYrnn%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%20to%20generate%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20speeches%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20simulating%20his%20voice%20calling%20for%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20cadres%20deployed%20WhatsApp%20and%20other%20electronic%20modalities%20in%20their%20get-out-the-vote%20efforts.%20The%20exercise%20was%20largely%20dismissed%20by%20the%20pundits%20and%20political%20opponents%20as%20mere%20social%20media%20hype.%20Not%20leaving%20anything%20to%20chance%2C%20the%20caretaker%20government%20had%20shut%20the%20mobile%20phone%20system%20and%20internet%20services%20on%20the%20polling%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fwas-there-anything-truly-historic-about-pakistans-2024-elections%5C%22%3EWas%20There%20Anything%20Truly%20Historic%20About%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%202024%20Elections%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20the%20preliminary%20results%20started%20coming%20in%2C%20the%20PTI-backed%20independents%20seemed%20unstoppable.%20While%20assorted%20television%20and%20news%20outlets%20were%20making%20projections%2C%20the%20official%20provisional%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-02-08%2Fpakistan-poll-results-delayed-as-imran-khan-s-party-claims-win%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-02-08%2Fpakistan-poll-results-delayed-as-imran-khan-s-party-claims-win%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw051-FMTITb6FAJ2mWRCand%5C%22%3Eresults%20were%20nowhere%20to%20be%20found%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20was%20seen%20as%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20old%20tactic%20of%20tinkering%20with%20the%20election%20results%20when%20it%20fails%20to%20achieve%20the%20desired%20outcome%20through%20pre-poll%20rigging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Pashtun%20and%20Baloch%20nationalist%20parties%20cried%20foul.%20They%20alleged%20gross%20discrepancies%20between%20the%20vote%20count%20submitted%20by%20the%20presiding%20officers%20at%20the%20polling%20stations%20and%20the%20consolidated%20results%20released%20by%20the%20returning%20officers%20at%20the%20constituency%20level.%20But%20it%20all%20seemed%20like%20an%20amateur%20hour%20at%20the%20establishment%E2%80%99s%20rigging%20headquarters%2C%20which%20was%20playing%20catch-up%20to%20stymie%20the%20PTI%E2%80%99s%20outright%20victory.%20Khan%2C%20however%2C%20declared%20triumph%20%E2%80%93%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F02%2F11%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fimran-khan-artificial-intelligence-pakistan.html%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F02%2F11%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fimran-khan-artificial-intelligence-pakistan.html%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1v0-jUbI5GdHpT5QPM85GM%5C%22%3Espeech%20generated%20by%20A.I%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20visibly%20crestfallen%20Nawaz%20Sharif%2C%20who%20was%20seeking%20a%20fourth%20stint%20as%20the%20PM%2C%20also%20a%20made%20a%20subdued%20speech%20proclaiming%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%E2%80%99s%20remarkable%20bounce%20back%20was%20a%20culmination%20of%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20relentless%20assault%20on%20his%20opponents%20since%20his%20ouster%20from%20power%20in%20April%202022%20through%20a%20no-confidence%20move%2C%20which%20also%20had%20a%20nod%20from%20the%20then%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%20(COAS)%20Qamar%20Javed%20Bajwa.%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20dogged%20offensive%20targeted%20both%20Bajwa%20and%20his%20successor%2C%20General%20Asim%20Munir%20along%20the%20way.%20When%20the%20PTI%20chief%20was%20eventually%20arrested%2C%20his%20party%20men%20even%20rioted%20against%20military%20installations%20for%20which%20both%20the%20leader%20and%20cadres%20are%20facing%20charges.%20But%20an%20undeterred%20Khan%20didn%E2%80%99t%20back%20down%20from%20railing%20against%20General%20Munir.%20He%20also%20trained%20his%20guns%20on%20the%20Pakistan%20Democratic%20Movement%20(PDM)%20coalition%20government%20comprising%20of%20the%20PMLN%20and%20the%20PPP%20that%20had%20replaced%20him%20and%20scored%20several%20bye-election%20victories%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%20is%20a%20textbook%20demagogue%20who%20thrived%20in%20turmoil%20and%20successfully%20channeled%20the%20existing%20dislike%20for%20traditional%20politics%20and%20widespread%20resentment%20against%20the%20army%2C%20to%20mobilise%20his%20cult-like%20following%2C%20especially%20among%20the%20young%20voters%20that%20make%20the%20bulk%20of%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20electorate.%20The%20results%2C%20however%2C%20also%20suggest%20pockets%20of%20support%20for%20Khan%20in%20the%20state%20machinery%2C%20including%20the%20army%2C%20which%20might%20have%20been%20a%20hurdle%20in%20the%20establishment%E2%80%99s%20plan%20to%20completely%20steamroll%20the%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20election%20that%20was%20essentially%20fought%20along%20the%20pro%20and%20anti-Imran%20Khan%20line%2C%20the%20traditional%20political%20forces%20largely%20played%20catch%20up%20with%20him.%20The%20PMLN%2C%20despite%20securing%20a%20majority%20in%20its%20traditional%20bastion%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20provincial%20legislature%2C%20performed%20dismally%20at%20the%20national%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENawaz%20Sharif%2C%20who%20had%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-67167601%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-67167601%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw04dgkXPYTFmj_uk-CNOOMo%5C%22%3Ereturned%20from%20a%20self-exile%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20London%20last%20October%2C%20to%20lead%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20campaign%2C%20could%20not%20lift%20its%20sagging%20fortunes.%20He%20had%20tried%20to%20put%20himself%20between%20the%20electorate%20and%20the%20Shehbaz%20Sharif-led%20PDM%20government%E2%80%99s%20abysmal%20performance%2C%20during%20which%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fasia.nikkei.com%2FEconomy%2FInflation%2FPakistan-inflation-hits-record-35-as-IMF-talks-drag-on%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fasia.nikkei.com%2FEconomy%2FInflation%2FPakistan-inflation-hits-record-35-as-IMF-talks-drag-on%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw35FrdaZb8TbKboGIr-5syj%5C%22%3Einflation%20had%20risen%20to%2035%25%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20Pakistan%20narrowly%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-07-12%2Fpakistan-secures-final-imf-approval-for-3-billion-bailout%23xj4y7vzkg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-07-12%2Fpakistan-secures-final-imf-approval-for-3-billion-bailout%2523xj4y7vzkg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1oHyItTNYX449cJg-5gpTQ%5C%22%3Edodged%20the%20economic%20default%20bullet%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20the%20campaign%20trail%2C%20Sharif%2C%20ostensibly%20under%20pressure%20from%20his%20own%20brother%20and%20other%20partymen%2C%20opted%20to%20shelve%20his%20previous%20anti-establishment%20plank%20and%20avoided%20questioning%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20meddling%20in%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20combined%20weight%20of%20PDM%2FPMLN%E2%80%99s%2016-month%20incumbency%2C%20reliance%20on%201990s-style%20patronage%20politics%2C%20and%20abandoning%20a%20principled%20position%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20the%20army%2C%20was%20too%20much%20even%20for%20Sharif%20to%20pull.%20Pashtun%20and%20Baloch%20nationalist%20forces%2C%20which%20had%20entered%20the%20field%20divided%20into%20several%20parties%20and%20groups%2C%20also%20faced%20the%20brunt%20of%20rigging%2C%20especially%20in%20Balochistan%20and%20the%20former%20tribal%20districts%20of%20KP%2C%20where%20assorted%20pro-army%20candidates%20got%20the%20results%20fixed%20in%20their%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Muttahida%20Qaumi%20Movement%20(MQM)%2C%20which%20claims%20to%20represent%20the%20Urdu-speaking%20population%20of%20urban%20Sindh%2C%20appears%20to%20have%20benefitted%20from%20the%20establishment%20trying%20to%20offset%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20lead%20in%20Punjab%20and%20KP%2C%20and%20got%20awarded%20a%20handful%20of%20seats.%20The%20only%20traditional%20party%20that%20escaped%20rather%20unscathed%20was%20the%20former%20president%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari%20and%20his%20son%20Bilawal%20Bhutto%E2%80%99s%20PPP.%20The%20PPP%20has%20perfected%20the%20art%20of%20positioning%20itself%20as%20a%20Sindhi%20nationalist%20party%20in%20its%20home%20province%20while%20posturing%20as%20the%20great%20federalist%20force%20at%20the%20center.%20It%20was%20able%20to%20retain%20a%20not%20only%20a%20comfortable%20majority%20in%20Sindh%20province%2C%20but%20also%20made%20inroads%20in%20Balochistan%20by%20enlisting%20several%20army-allied%20tribal%20politicians.%20The%20PPP%20was%20perhaps%20the%20only%20party%20that%20actually%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPPP_Org%2Fstatus%2F1759292948393402840%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPPP_Org%2Fstatus%2F1759292948393402840%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1OQa4ehQ9iSYaZ8Bnpe6LA%5C%22%3Ecelebrated%20Yaum-e-Tashakkur%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0or%20a%20thanksgiving%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20all%20said%20and%20done%2C%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20the%20PTI%20won%2093%20seats%2C%20the%20PML-N%2075%2C%20the%20PPP%2054%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20MQM%20at%2017%20seats.%20Several%20ethno-nationalist%20and%20religious%20parties%20are%20in%20single%20digits.%20It%20is%20effectively%20a%20hung%20parliament%20with%20no%20party%20in%20a%20position%20to%20form%20the%20government%20on%20its%20own%2C%20let%20alone%20the%20PTI%20with%20Khan%20in%20no%20mood%20to%20negotiate%20with%20the%20others.%20The%20PTI-backed%20independent%20candidates%20are%20further%20hamstrung%20by%20the%20stipulation%20that%20unless%20they%20join%20a%20formal%20party%20that%20has%20presence%20in%20the%20national%20assembly%2C%20they%20would%20be%20deprived%20of%20the%20seats%20reserved%20for%20the%20women%20and%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PMLN%20and%20the%20PPP%20played%20hot%20potato%20with%20the%20government%20formation%2C%20knowing%20full%20well%20that%20this%20dispensation%20won%E2%80%99t%20exactly%20be%20a%20bed%20of%20roses.%20Unwilling%20to%20sit%20atop%20a%20shaky%20government%20at%20the%20twilight%20of%20his%20political%20career%2C%20Sharif%20had%20pulled%20himself%20out%20of%20the%20race%20for%20the%20high%20office.%20He%20nominated%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%2C%20a%20known%20toady%20of%20the%20army%2C%20for%20the%20slot.%20The%20PPP%2C%20in%20a%20better%20position%20than%20ever%20to%20exact%20its%20pound%20of%20flesh%2C%20played%20hard%20to%20catch%20for%20a%20bit.%20But%20finally%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenews.com.pk%2Flatest%2F1159717-bilawal-addresses-presser-after-days-long-ppp-pml-n-govt-formation-meeting%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenews.com.pk%2Flatest%2F1159717-bilawal-addresses-presser-after-days-long-ppp-pml-n-govt-formation-meeting%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1708667844882000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1so3Msxdl4AWRNaAydi-Jp%5C%22%3Ecoalition%20government%20was%20announced%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0with%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20as%20the%20PM%2C%20in%20exchange%20for%20Asif%20Zardari%20becoming%20the%20president%20and%20assorted%20elected%20and%20appointed%20offices%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Balochistan%20government%20likely%20going%20to%20the%20PPP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20setup%20is%20essentially%20the%20second%20edition%20of%20the%20PDM%20coalition%20that