2FGaza%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20type%20of%20world%20do%20we%20live%20in%20when%20health%20workers%20are%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20bombed%20as%20they%20carry%20out%20their%20life%20saving%20work%3F%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWHO%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40WHO%3C%2Fa%3E%20chief%2C%20Tedros%20Ghebreyesus%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5jvKyx8lBm%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F5jvKyx8lBm%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20UN%20News%20(%40UN_News_Centre)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUN_News_Centre%2Fstatus%2F1760341232029458762%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2021%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHospital%20evacuations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20three%20days%2C%20the%20UN%20health%20agency%20and%20partners%20carried%20out%20several%20emergency%20missions%20to%20the%20Nasser%20medical%20complex%20in%20Khan%20Younis%2C%20southern%20Gaza%2C%20to%20evacuate%20critically%20ill%20patients%2C%20including%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20intensive%20care%20units%20no%20longer%20working%2C%20WHO%20helped%20move%20patients%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20cannot%20even%20walk%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tedros%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20130%20sick%20and%20injured%20patients%20and%20at%20least%2015%20doctors%20and%20nurses%20remain%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20amidst%20ongoing%20Israeli%20military%20operations%2C%20no%20electricity%20and%20running%20water%20and%20dwindling%20lifesaving%20medical%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImplement%20%E2%80%98long%20overdue%E2%80%99%20measures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20UN%20independent%20human%20rights%20experts%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Fpress-releases%2F2024%2F02%2Fgaza-un-experts-call-prioritisation-gender-responsive-humanitarian%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalled%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20Israel%20to%20urgently%20implement%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20and%20concrete%20humanitarian%20measures%2C%20with%20a%20particular%20focus%20on%20the%20needs%20of%20Palestinian%20women%20and%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icj-cij.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EICJ%3C%2Fa%3E)%E2%80%99s%20January%2026%20ruling%2C%20the%20experts%20underscored%20the%20pressing%20issues%20of%20disrupted%20schooling%2C%20destruction%20of%20homes%2C%20limited%20access%20to%20healthcare%20and%20heightened%20risks%20faced%20by%20women%20and%20girls%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F02%2F1146667%5C%22%3Egender-based%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20increasingly%20limited%20access%20to%20treatment%2C%20the%20experts%20demanded%20an%20end%20to%20Israeli%20forces%E2%80%99%20attacks%20on%20hospitals%2C%20emphasizing%20the%20need%20for%20gender-responsive%20measures%20to%20address%20the%20urgent%20needs%20of%20the%20vulnerable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20specifically%20called%20for%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20field%20hospital%2C%20facilitation%20of%20aid%20delivery%2C%20prioritization%20of%20menstrual%20hygiene%20products%2C%20building%20additional%20shelters%20and%20schools%20and%20providing%20safe%20spaces%20for%20survivors%20of%20gender-based%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CImplementing%20these%20measures%20would%20be%20a%20long%20overdue%20demonstration%20that%20Israel%20cares%20about%20the%20protection%20of%20civilians%20and%20respects%20their%20human%20rights%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppointed%20by%20the%20UN%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2FEN%2FHRBodies%2FHRC%2FPages%2FHome.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHuman%20Rights%20Council%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20monitor%20key%20human%20rights%20issues%2C%20the%20experts%20are%20independent%20of%20the%20UN%20or%20any%20government%2C%20serve%20in%20their%20individual%20capacities%20and%20draw%20no%20salary%20for%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGazans%20%E2%80%98hanging%20by%20a%20thread%E2%80%99%2C%20warns%20WFP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20UN%20World%20Food%20Programme%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww1.wfp.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWFP%3C%2Fa%3E)%20said%20it%20has%20reluctantly%20had%20to%20pause%20aid%20deliveries%20to%20north%20Gaza%20until%20conditions%20are%20in%20place%20that%20allow%20for%20safe%20distributions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20decision%20to%20pause%20deliveries%20to%20the%20north%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20has%20not%20been%20taken%20lightly%2C%20as%20we%20know%20it%20means%20the%20situation%20there%20will%20deteriorate%20further%20and%20more%20people%20risk%20dying%20of%20hunger%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20committed%E2%80%9D%20to%20urgently%20reaching%20desperate%20people%20across%20the%20war-torn%20enclave%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20to%20deliver%20critical%20food%20aid%20%E2%80%93%20and%20for%20the%20people%20receiving%20it%20%E2%80%93%20must%20be%20ensured%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20the%20UN%20and%20humanitarian%20partners%20had%20warned%20of%20the%20risk%20of%20famine%20in%20northern%20Gaza%20by%20May%20unless%20conditions%20there%20improved%20decisively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20particularly%20dire%20for%20children%2C%20pregnant%20women%20and%20new%20mothers%2C%20with%20one%20in%20six%20children%20acutely%20malnourished.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Facing%20gunfire%20and%20explosive%20anger%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWFP%20said%20that%20its%20deliveries%20to%20northern%20Gaza%20had%20resumed%20on%20Sunday%20after%20a%20three-week%20suspension%20following%20the%20strike%20on%20an%20UN%20Palestine%20relief%20agency%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unrwa.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUNRWA%3C%2Fa%3E)%20truck%20and%20due%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20functioning%20humanitarian%20notification%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FGaza%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20type%20of%20world%20do%20we%20live%20in%20when%20health%20workers%20are%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20bombed%20as%20they%20carry%20out%20their%20life%20saving%20work%3F%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWHO%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40WHO%3C%2Fa%3E%20chief%2C%20Tedros%20Ghebreyesus%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5jvKyx8lBm%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F5jvKyx8lBm%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20UN%20News%20(%40UN_News_Centre)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUN_News_Centre%2Fstatus%2F1760341232029458762%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2021%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20as%20one%20of%20its%20convoys%20moved%20towards%20Gaza%20City%2C%20it%20was%20surrounded%20by%20crowds%20of%20hungry%20people%20close%20to%20the%20Wadi%20Gaza%20checkpoint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%20fending%20off%20multiple%20attempts%20by%20people%20trying%20to%20climb%20aboard%20our%20trucks%2C%20then%20facing%20gunfire%20once%20we%20entered%20Gaza%20City%2C%20our%20team%20was%20able%20to%20distribute%20a%20small%20quantity%20of%20the%20food%20along%20the%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20UN%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20second%20convoy%E2%80%99s%20journey%20north%20faced%20%E2%80%9Ccomplete%20chaos%20and%20violence%E2%80%9D%20due%20to%20the%20collapse%20of%20civil%20order%2C%20WFP%20added%2C%20noting%20that%20several%20trucks%20were%20looted%20between%20Khan%20Younis%20and%20Deir%20al%20Balah%20and%20a%20truck%20driver%20was%20beaten.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20remaining%20flour%20was%20spontaneously%20distributed%20off%20the%20trucks%20in%20Gaza%20city%2C%20amidst%20high%20tension%20and%20explosive%20anger.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUrgent%20effort%20to%20restore%20aid%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20statement%2C%20WFP%20emphasized%20that%20it%20will%20seek%20ways%20to%20resume%20deliveries%20in%20a%20responsible%20manner%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20underscored%20the%20need%20%E2%80%9Csignificantly%E2%80%9D%20higher%20volumes%20of%20food%20coming%20into%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20from%20multiple%20routes%2C%20and%20for%20crossing%20points%20to%20the%20north%20of%20Gaza%20to%20be%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20functioning%20humanitarian%20notification%20system%20and%20a%20stable%20communication%20network%20are%20needed.%20And%20security%2C%20for%20our%20staff%20and%20partners%20as%20well%20as%20for%20the%20people%20we%20serve%2C%20must%20be%20facilitated%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGaza%20is%20hanging%20by%20a%20thread%20and%20WFP%20must%20be%20enabled%20to%20reverse%20the%20path%20towards%20famine%20for%20thousands%20of%20desperately%20hungry%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEvacuations%20from%20Nasser%20Hospital%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20UN%20World%20Health%20Organization%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWHO%3C%2Fa%3E)%20continued%20evacuating%20patients%20from%20the%20Nasser%20hospital%20complex%20in%20Khan%20Younis%2C%20amid%20continuing%20Israeli%20military%20operations%20and%20access%20restrictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20health%20agency%20led%20two%20successful%20missions%2C%20evacuating%2032%20critical%20patients%2C%20including%20two%20children%2C%20from%20the%20complex%20on%20Sunday%20and%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high-risk%20missions%20were%20conducted%20in%20close%20partnership%20with%20the%20Palestine%20Red%20Crescent%20Society%20(PRCS)%20and%20the%20UN%20Office%20for%20the%20Coordination%20of%20Humanitarian%20Affairs%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unocha.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOCHA%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20at%20the%20hospital%20continues%20to%20remain%20dire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20no%20electricity%20or%20running%20water%2C%20and%20medical%20waste%20and%20garbage%20are%20creating%20a%20breeding%20ground%20for%20disease.%2C%20WHO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStaff%20said%20the%20destruction%20around%20the%20hospital%20was%20%E2%80%9Cindescribable%E2%80%9D%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20area%20was%20surrounded%20by%20burnt%20and%20destroyed%20buildings%2C%20heavy%20layers%20of%20debris%2C%20with%20no%20road%20accessible%20roads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThese%20articles%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F02%2F1146792%5C%22%3EWHO%20chief%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F02%2F1146702%5C%22%3EWorld%20Food%20Programme%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E)%20were%20originally%20published%20by%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2F%5C%22%3EUN%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708595952000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08150335%2Fimage560x340cropped.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fgaza-has-become-a-death-zone-who-chief-as-29000-killed-in-israeli-bombing%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20UN%20World%20Food%20Programme%20(WFP)%20said%20it%20has%20reluctantly%20had%20to%20pause%20aid%20deliveries%20to%20north%20Gaza%20until%20conditions%20are%20in%20place%20that%20allow%20for%20safe%20distributions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fgaza-has-become-a-death-zone-who-chief-as-29000-killed-in-israeli-bombing%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biden%20calling%20Putin%20'crazy%20SOB'%20debases%20US%3A%20Kremlin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708595658000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107912059%2Cimgsize-29878.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fbidens-crazy-sob-remark-debases-us-kremlin%2Farticleshow%2F107911290.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107911290.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20Kremlin%20criticizes%20Joe%20Biden's%20derogatory%20remarks%20about%20Vladimir%20Putin%2C%20suggesting%20they%20are%20an%20attempt%20to%20portray%20himself%20as%20a%20Hollywood%20cowboy.%20Dmitry%20Medvedev%20escalates%20tensions%20by%20mentioning%20Ukraine.%20Strained%20Russia-West%20relationship%20due%20to%20Ukraine%20and%20Navalny's%20death.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fbidens-crazy-sob-remark-debases-us-kremlin%2Farticleshow%2F107911290.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fbidens-crazy-sob-remark-debases-us-kremlin%2Famp_articleshow%2F107911290.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fbidens-crazy-sob-remark-debases-us-kremlin%2Famp_articleshow%2F107911290.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20India's%20COVID%20Lockdowns%20Impacted%20Menstrual%20Health%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F22124958%2Fnatracare-r7UjnJHJxmY-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIndian%20women%20used%20far%20fewer%20sanitary%20pads%2C%20tampons%20and%20other%20period%20products%20during%20COVID-19%20lockdowns%20%E2%80%94%20with%20those%20items%20becoming%20hard%20to%20access%20due%20to%20not%20being%20initially%20included%20on%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffeminisminindia.com%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2Fcovid-19-lockdown-sanitary-products-not-deemed-essential%2F%5C%22%3Eessential%20items%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20in%20the%20red%20zones%20%E2%80%94%20the%20districts%20under%20the%20strictest%20lockdown%20measures%20%E2%80%94%20research%20reveals%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspssi.onlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1111%2Fjosi.12533%5C%22%3Ea%2053%20percent%20decline%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20the%20distribution%20of%20sanitary%20pads%20to%20adolescent%20girls%2C%20compared%20to%20girls%20in%20green%20zones%20under%20the%20lightest%20lockdown%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsumption%20dropped%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F00036846.2023.2257035%5C%22%3E16%20per%20cent%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20the%20most%20strictly%20locked-down%20districts%20of%20India%20during%202020.%20In%20rural%20districts%20alone%2C%20it%20dropped%2025%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAccessing%20pads%20in%20the%20lockdown%20was%20a%20major%20crisis%20for%20us%20in%20the%20village%20because%20the%20shops%20in%20the%20market%20were%20shut%20and%20there%20was%20no%20other%20source%20to%20avail%20it%20from%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%2019-year-old%20living%20in%20the%20village%20of%20Hardiya%20in%20the%20eastern%20state%20of%20Bihar%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F13691058.2023.2287723%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20solution%20was%20to%20band%20together%20with%20a%20group%20of%20friends%20to%20try%20to%20source%20the%20products%20for%20their%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20period%20products%20soared%20during%20lockdowns%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20disposable%20pads%20were%20not%20available%20easily%2C%20this%20led%20to%20black%20marketing%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%2027-year-old%20professional%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F13691058.2023.2287723%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20pay%20almost%20double%20the%20price%20to%20procure%20the%20product.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amwa-doc.org%2Fperiod-poverty%2F%5C%22%3EPeriod%20poverty%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20the%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20resources%20and%20education%20linked%20to%20menstrual%20health%20and%20hygiene%2C%20including%20essential%20items%20like%20period%20products%2C%20washing%20facilities%2C%20and%20proper%20waste%20management%20%E2%80%94%20has%20long%20been%20a%20pressing%20concern%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20roots%20can%20be%20traced%20back%20to%20patriarchal%20notions%20that%20label%20menstruation%20as%20impure%20and%20dirty%2C%20restricting%20the%20freedom%20of%20those%20who%20menstruate%20during%20their%20periods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20global%20recognition%20of%20menstrual%20health%20as%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flanpub%2Farticle%2FPIIS2468-2667(21)00212-7%2Ffulltext%5C%22%3Epublic%20health%20and%20human%20rights%20issue%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3Eperiod%20poverty%20continues%20to%20taint%20the%20experiences%20of%20the%20individuals%20who%20menstruate%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20prompted%20the%20government%20to%20initiate%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhm.gov.in%2Findex1.php%3Flang%3D1%26level%3D3%26sublinkid%3D1021%26lid%3D391%5C%22%3EMenstrual%20Hygiene%20Scheme%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%202011%20for%20adolescent%20girls%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%20involves%20distribution%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnhm.gov.in%2Findex1.php%3Flang%3D1%26level%3D2%26sublinkid%3D818%26lid%3D221%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520order%2520to%2520ensure%2520holistic%2Cout%252Dof%252Dschool%2520adolescents%2520with%5C%22%3Esanitary%20pads%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0alongside%20educational%20programmes%20on%20menstrual%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20exacerbated%20period%20poverty%2C%20primarily%20due%20to%20the%20widespread%20job%20losses%20and%20financial%20difficulties%20resulting%20from%20extended%20quarantines%20and%20business%20closure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lockdown%20impacted%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspssi.onlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1111%2Fjosi.12533%5C%22%3Edistribution%20of%20sanitary%20pads%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0under%20the%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1080%2F00036846.2023.2257035%5C%22%3Econsumption%20of%20period%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0was%20also%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedia%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-52718434%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0highlighted%20period%20poverty%20during%20the%20pandemic%20in%20India%2C%20attributing%20it%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffeminisminindia.com%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2Fcovid-19-lockdown-sanitary-products-not-deemed-essential%2F%5C%22%3Edelayed%20inclusion%20of%20the%20period%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20the%20essentials%20list%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20lockdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20factors%20contributed%20to%20the%20decline%2C%20including%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fvoices%2Fwomen%2Fcoronavirus-asha-women-financial-support-recognition%5C%22%3Eadministrative%20delays%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0for%20getting%20work%20permits%2C%20labour%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1007%2Fs41027-020-00293-8%5C%22%3Eshortages%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0due%20to%20migration%20and%20the%20reallocation%20of%20social%20workers%20to%20COVID%20related%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20overall%20they%20showed%20a%20gap%20in%20the%20healthcare%20system%20to%20address%20this%20gender%20equity%20divide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20challenges%20forced%20women%20and%20other%20people%20who%20menstruate%20to%20use%20the%20same%20period%20products%20for%20extended%20periods%20or%20resort%20to%20alternatives%20including%20clothes%20and%20rags.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20effect%20on%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aa.com.tr%2Fen%2Fasia-pacific%2Findia-faces-sanitary-napkin-shortage-amid-covid-19%2F1855047%5C%22%3Emenstrual%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0was%20acute%2C%20including%20irregular%20menstrual%20cycles%2C%20heavy%20bleeding%2C%20and%20infections%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20genital%20tract-related%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20disaster-like%20situations%2C%20individuals%20who%20menstruate%20often%20find%20themselves%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20priority%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20pandemic%2C%20resources%20were%20diverted%20to%20combat%20the%20virus%2C%20leaving%20period%20products%20unavailable%20and%20inaccessible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20led%20to%20compromised%20menstrual%20health%2C%20exacerbating%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F13691058.2023.2287723%5C%22%3Estress%20and%20anxiety%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0among%20those%20who%20menstruate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrioritising%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20individuals%20who%20menstruate%2C%20especially%20in%20emergency-related%20situations%2C%20is%20imperative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20forward%2C%20there%20are%20specific%20measures%20the%20government%20and%20policymakers%20could%20take%20to%20support%20menstrual%20health%20and%20hygiene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20include%20ensuring%20the%20availability%20and%20accessibility%20of%20period%20products%20during%20emergencies%20and%20%C2%A0incentivising%20manufacturers%20working%20in%20the%20similar%20industry%20to%20start%20making%20period%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20could%20also%20conduct%20public%20health%20communication%20campaigns%20via%20mass%20media%20and%20social%20media%20channels%20to%20dispel%20taboos%20and%20myths%20surrounding%20menstruation%2C%20and%20improve%20measures%20for%20effective%20menstrual%20health%20and%20hygiene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20taking%20these%20steps%2C%20India%20and%20other%20countries%20can%20work%20towards%20a%20more%20inclusive%20and%20supportive%20environment%20for%20individuals%20who%20menstruate%2C%20especially%20during%20challenging%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fiima.ac.in%2Fkaran-babbar%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Ci%3EDr%20Karan%20Babbar%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0is%20an%20Assistant%20Professor%20at%20Jindal%20Global%20Business%20School%2C%20OP%20Jindal%20Global%20University.%20His%20research%20sits%20at%20the%20intersection%20of%20education%2C%20health%20and%20gender.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EOriginally%20published%20under%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcreativecommons.org%2Flicenses%2Fby%2F4.0%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ECreative%20Commons%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0by%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F360info.org%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E360info%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%E2%84%A2.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708594233000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F221249