Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOf%20wall%20paintings%20and%20a%20library%20of%20magic%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20when%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20Gopal%20found%20the%20perfect%20opportunity%20to%20make%20use%20of%20his%20free%20time.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20to%20plant%20saplings%20all%20around%20the%20school%20so%20that%20it%20blooms%20into%20a%20garden%20when%20it%20is%20time%20for%20students%20to%20come%20back.%20Since%20there%20was%20no%20water%20connection%20in%20the%20school%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20buy%20a%20tanker%20of%20water%20to%20maintain%20the%20garden%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tanker%20would%20cost%20about%20Rs%20300%20and%20would%20last%20for%20a%20week.%20Calling%20himself%20an%20%E2%80%9Cartist%E2%80%9D%20of%20sorts%2C%20he%20says%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20fun%20with%20the%20walls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20walls%20were%20mundane%20and%20not%20fit%20for%20a%20school.%20I%20wanted%20to%20paint%20animals%2C%20birds%2C%20murals%20and%20whatnot%20on%20them.%20I%20undertook%20the%20task%20of%20making%20the%20place%20the%20most%20colourful%20building%20in%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20entering%20the%20school%20now%2C%20one%20is%20no%20longer%20greeted%20by%20a%20shabby-looking%20building%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20as%20if%20a%20rainbow%20itself%20has%20splashed%20colours%20onto%20the%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGopal%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20cleaned%20up%20the%20surroundings%20of%20the%20school%20and%20adorned%20the%20walls%2C%20and%20even%20the%20ceilings%2C%20with%20colourful%20paints%2C%20creating%20images%20and%20inscribing%20inspirational%20messages.%20The%20outcome%20was%20a%20cheerful%2C%20radiant%2C%20and%20lively%20environment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2