caption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHygenco%20has%20announced%20plans%20to%20construct%20and%20operate%20a%20100%20percent%20green%20hydrogen%20plant%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20working%20in%20the%20renewable%20energy%20sector%2C%20Amit%20wanted%20to%20work%20towards%20addressing%20India%E2%80%99s%20energy%20crises.%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20a%20fast-growing%20country%2C%20which%20is%20also%20increasing%20the%20use%20of%20fossil%20fuels.%20Since%20the%20country%20is%20significantly%20dependent%20on%20imports%20for%20its%20energy%20needs%2C%20there%20is%20a%20very%20strong%20business%20sense%20for%20harnessing%20the%20power%20of%20green%20hydrogen%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%2039-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20why%20India%20needs%20green%20hydrogen%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSome%20of%20the%20major%20factors%20why%20we%20feel%20India%20needs%20green%20hydrogen%20include%2C%20energy%20independence%2C%20achieving%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20net%20zero%20targets%2C%20and%20creating%20huge%20job%20opportunities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20save%20our%20forex.%20The%20precious%20foreign%20exchange%20saved%20by%20reducing%20fossil%20fuel%20imports%20can%20be%20harnessed%20for%20social%20use%20such%20as%20health%20and%20education.%20Further%2C%20the%20country%20can%20even%20target%20to%20become%20a%20net%20exporter%20of%20ammonia%20and%20its%20derivatives%20from%20being%20a%20large%20importer%20of%20fossil%20fuels%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20Amit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CGreen%20hydrogen%20and%20its%20derivatives%20as%20fuel%20can%20decarbonise%20hard-to-abate%20sectors%2C%20especially%20since%20these%20sectors%20contribute%20nearly%2080%20percent%20of%20carbon%20footprint.%20This%20will%20be%20crucial%20as%20conventional%20electricity%20replacement%20by%20100%20percent%20green%20electricity%20will%20only%20