%20suitcase%20he%2Fshe%20purchases!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opacity%20in%20the%20donation%20gambit%20is%20thus%20erased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fdonate-to-ngos-2-1707998753.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Share%20At%20Door%20Step%20is%20present%20in%2011%20countries%20and%20has%20recently%20also%20extended%20its%20services%20to%20Singapore%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fdonate-to-ngos-2-1707998753.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fdonate-to-ngos-2-1707998753-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fdonate-to-ngos-2-1707998753-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fdonate-to-ngos-2-1707998753-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fdonate-to-ngos-2-1707998753-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341912%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShare%20At%20Door%20Step%20is%20present%20in%2011%20countries%20and%20has%20recently%20also%20extended%20its%20services%20to%20Singapore%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Anushka%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20individuals%20who%20wish%20to%20donate%20items%2C%20the%20process%20is%20simple%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGo%20to%20our%20website%2C%20book%20a%20pickup%20based%20on%20your%20city%20and%20location%2C%20register%20the%20item%20you%E2%80%99re%20looking%20to%20donate%20and%20also%20mention%20if%20it%20is%20light%20(small%20items%20like%20bags%2C%20purses%2C%20clothes)%20or%20heavy%20(large%20suitcases%2C%20decor%20and%20furnishing%20items%2C%20etc)%20an